e-documentary-in-the-clutch-1235881987%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fsue-bird-sundance-documentary-in-the-clutch-1235881987%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20dreamed%20of%20the%20travel%20we'd%20do%20as%20a%20family%20of%204.%20Then%20came%20my%20youngest%20daughter's%20life-altering%20diagnosis.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20and%20daughter%20with%20Sydney%20Harbour%20Bridge%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ade9b2dcdb354a98597f67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuthor%20and%20her%20eldest%20daughter%20on%20vacation%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Sydney.%3Cp%3ETatyana%20Leonov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETatyana%20Leonov%20and%20her%20eldest%20daughter%20take%20a%20trip%20alone%20together%20once%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20her%20younger%20child%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Angelman%20syndrome%2C%20a%20rare%20neurogenetic%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trips%20have%20helped%20strengthen%20the%20whole%20family's%20bond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hadn't%20even%20checked%20in%20yet%2C%20and%20my%204-year-old%20daughter's%20hands%20were%20full%20of%20sweets.%20It%20took%20her%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20to%20discover%20the%20help-yourself%20candy%20bar%20near%20the%20check-in%20counter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-friendly-trips-asia-australia-tips-where-to-go-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESydney's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ovolo%20Woolloommooloo%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20my%20oldest%20daughter%20and%20I%20had%20traveled%20together%20as%20a%20duo%20since%20the%20birth%20of%20my%20second%20child.%20That%20trip%20was%20almost%20three%20years%20ago%20now%2C%20and%20we've%20made%20it%20a%20tradition.%20Although%20it's%20tough%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20my%20husband%20and%20baby%20girl%2C%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-on-one-time-children-mother-daughter-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-on-one%20time%20has%20become%20essential%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20at%208%20months%20old%2C%20our%20youngest%20child%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20rare%20neurogenetic%20condition%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcureangelman.org.au%2Fwhat-is-angelman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAngelman%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20complex%20disorder%20primarily%20affects%20the%20nervous%20system%20and%20causes%20significant%20delays%20in%20almost%20all%20aspects%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turned%20our%20lives%20upside%20down%20and%20most%20days%20now%20are%20a%20challenge.%20We%20find%20ourselves%20very%20time-constrained%20as%20she%20attends%20multiple%20therapies%20every%20week%20and%20deals%20with%20complex%20medical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20suburban%20Sydney%2C%20and%20with%20so%20many%20therapies%20and%20appointments%2C%20I%20spend%20long%20chunks%20of%20the%20day%20in%20the%20car%20getting%20our%20little%20one%20from%20A%20to%20B%20(and%20often%20C%2C%20D%2C%20E%2C%20and%20F).%20Thankfully%2C%20we%20have%20supportive%20family%20members%20and%20friends%20who%20help%20from%20time%20to%20time%20with%20shuttling%20my%20eldest%20to%20her%20many%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENew%20dreams%20and%20new%20plans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20girl%20dancing%20with%20clowns%20and%20amusement%20park%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ae0e5e617029e90a5ee06f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20eldest%20daughter's%20first%20%26quot%3BYes%20Day%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20theme%20park%20in%20Sydney.%3Cp%3ETatyana%20Leonov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20our%20original%20dreams%20have%20been%20shattered%20(most%20people%20with%20Angelman%20syndrome%20require%20lifelong%20care%2C%20and%20are%20not%20able%20to%20do%20things%20like%20go%20camping%20with%20friends%2C%20get%20a%20job%2C%20or%20find%20a%20partner)%2C%20we've%20crafted%20new%20ones%20and%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20the%20things%20we%20imagined%20we%20would%20do%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20of%20us%20still%20manage%20to%20travel%20together%20and%20visit%20the%20same%20locations%20as%20before%20D-Day%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nickname%20used%20within%20the%20special%20needs%20community%20for%20Diagnosis%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20demanding%3A%20Trips%20with%20all%20four%20of%20us%20include%20special%20gear%20like%20a%20safety%20bed%20and%20supportive%20seating.%20However%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20with%20love%20and%20support%2C%20children%20can%20navigate%20any%20situation%20with%20resilience%20and%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20at%20the%20hotel%20in%20Sydney%2C%20sugar%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20magic%20ingredient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20glanced%20around%20the%20lobby%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20marvel%20at%20the%20vibrant%2C%20eclectic%20d%C3%A9cor%20%E2%80%94%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20our%20usual%20serene%2C%20minimalist%20home%20environment.%20My%20daughter%2C%20wide-eyed%20and%20grinning%20with%20excitement%2C%20darted%20back%20to%20the%20candy%20bar%2C%20like%20a%20spirit%20possessed.%20I%20whisked%20her%20away%20and%20upstairs%20to%20our%20room%2C%20where%20a%20make-your-own%20popcorn%20machine%20beckoned.%20An%20hour%20later%2C%20she'd%20convinced%20me%20that%20the%20next%20day%20would%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-mom-lets-her-kid-skip-school-every-month-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BYes%20Day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20everything%20she%20asked%20for%20would%20be%20yes%20%E2%80%94%20while%20prioritizing%20safety.%20It%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20day%20of%20more%20sugar%20than%20I%20imagined%20possible%2C%20rides%20at%20the%20amusement%20park%2C%20and%20popcorn%20in%20bed%20while%20watching%20a%20movie.%20She%20still%20talks%20about%20this%20%26quot%3BYes%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20know%20that%20we%20created%20a%20special%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMaking%20memories%20and%20holiday%20traditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20travel%20writer%2C%20there%20are%20times%20when%20I'm%20given%20the%20chance%20to%20bring%20along%20a%20companion.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20this%20was%20typically%20my%20husband.%20More%20recently%2C%20I've%20been%20bringing%20along%20my%20eldest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20when%20my%20eldest%20was%206%2C%20I%20was%20sent%20on%20assignment%20to%20cover%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-christmas-cruise-vacation-home-for-holidays-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecruise%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20whole%20trip%20was%20six%20days%20long%2C%20with%20four%20spent%20on%20board%20the%20Celebrity%20Edge%20vessel.%20Although%20the%20trip%20was%20much%20longer%20than%20the%20previous%20vacations%20my%20daughter%20and%20I%20had%20taken%20together%2C%20it%20benefited%20the%20whole%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20were%20away%2C%20my%20mother-in-law%20spent%20the%20week%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20younger%20daughter.%20My%20eldest%20can%20head%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frules-for-grandparents-babysitting-looking-after-grandchildren-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrandparents'%20place%20for%20a%20sleepover%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that's%20far%20too%20challenging%20with%20my%20youngest%20%E2%80%94%20so%20a%20staycation%20with%20her%20grandma%20was%20the%20perfect%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20joy%20of%20%26quot%3BWants%20Nothing%26quot%3B%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother