0about%20affordability%2C%20not%20economic%20indicators.%20Opinion%20polls%20show%20that%20voters%20by%20a%20large%20margin%20view%20Republicans%20as%20better%20stewards%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20even%20though%20Trump%20has%20offered%20only%20vague%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESPEAKING%20TO%20FEAR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoters%20are%20unsettled%20for%20reasons%20that%20extend%20far%20beyond%20the%20economy.%20Trump%20speaks%20to%20the%20worries%2C%20real%20or%20not%2C%20that%20many%20white%20Americans%20have%20in%20a%20country%20that%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20diverse%20and%20more%20culturally%20progressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20pervasive%20sense%20of%20losing%20ground%2C%20that%20the%20cornerstones%20of%20American%20life%20-%20home%20ownership%2C%20a%20decent%20wage%20that%20keeps%20pace%20with%20inflation%2C%20a%20college%20education%20-%20are%20becoming%20more%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20many.%20Polls%20show%20voters%20are%20worried%20about%20crime%20and%20nervous%20about%20the%20flow%20of%20migrants%20crossing%20the%20U.S.-Mexico%20border%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20adept%20at%20channeling%20and%20packaging%20those%20fears%2C%20while%20still%20presenting%20himself%20as%20someone%20who%20comes%20from%20outside%20the%20U.S.%20political%20system.%20He%20is%20both%20arsonist%20and%20firefighter%2C%20who%20declares%20the%20country%20is%20in%20chaos%20and%20then%20offers%20himself%20as%20a%20savior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETRUMP'S%20ACTIONS%20NOT%20DISQUALIFYING%20FOR%20MANY%20VOTERS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20critics%20within%20his%20own%20party%2C%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20the%20media%20view%20him%20as%20unfit%20for%20office%2C%20millions%20of%20voters%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20many%20of%20his%20supporters%20have%20become%20convinced%20that%20Trump%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20political%20witch%20hunt.%20At%20least%20half%20of%20Republicans%2