0rebel%20group%20%26quot%3Bled%20a%20military%20operation%20targeting%20the%20American%20military%20cargo%20ship%20Ocean%20Jazz%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%2C%26quot%3B%20near%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20with%20missiles%2C%20said%20Huthi%20military%20spokesman%20Yahya%20Saree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20claim%2C%20a%20US%20defense%20official%20told%20AFP%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20seeing%20that%20at%20all%20on%20our%20end%20and%20believe%20that%20statement%20to%20be%20untrue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yemeni%20rebels%20began%20striking%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20in%20November%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20hitting%20Israeli-linked%20vessels%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20been%20ravaged%20by%20the%20Hamas-Israel%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Huthis%20have%20since%20declared%20American%20and%20British%20interests%20to%20be%20legitimate%20targets%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20military%20action%2C%20Washington%20is%20seeking%20to%20put%20diplomatic%20and%20financial%20pressure%20on%20the%20Huthis%2C%20re-designating%20them%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20entity%20last%20week%20after%20dropping%20that%20label%20soon%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20took%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebels%20reiterated%20on%20Monday%20that%20they%20will%20%26quot%3Brespond%20to%20any%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20Yemen%20and%20continue%20to%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20Israeli%20ships%26quot%3B%20from%20crossing%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYemen%20is%20just%20one%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20linked%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20Israel's%20relentless%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20offensive%20have%20killed%20at%20least%2025%2C295%20people%2C%20around%2070%20percent%20of%20them%20women%2C%20children%20and%20adolescents%2C%20according%20to%20the%20