dy%20looked%20at%20jobs%20where%20AI%20could%20be%20used%20for%20some%20sort%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-machine-learning-robotics-retail-supply-chain-technology-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20vision%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20replace%20regular%20human%20vision.%20The%20example%20they%20give%20in%20their%20paper%20is%20of%20a%20small%20bakery%2C%20where%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20the%20baker's%20job%20is%20to%20visually%20scan%20the%20flour%20and%20eggs%20before%20mixing%20them%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20haven't%20gone%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPotentially%2C%20the%20bakery%20could%20purchase%20a%20costly%20computer%20vision%20software%20system%2C%20but%20as%20the%20study%20reveals%20%E2%80%94and%20any%20bakery%20owner%20with%20a%20brain%20would%20know%20%E2%80%94%20this%20just%20doesn't%20make%20good%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20surveyed%20workers%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20many%20of%20their%20tasks%20were%20things%20that%20could%20be%20performed%20by%20computer%20vision%2C%20then%20made%20some%20models%20about%20cost%20effectiveness.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPretty%20much%20across%20the%20board%2C%20even%20for%20big%20companies%20like%20Walmart%2C%20they%20found%20that%20it%20would%20rarely%20be%20worth%20replacing%20workers%20with%20AI%20visual%20detection.%20From%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffuturetech-site.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com%2F2024-01-18%2BBeyond_AI_Exposure.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20find%20that%20the%20median%20employee%20works%20in%20a%20firm%20where%20close%20to%20none%20of%20the%20vision%20tasks%20are%20cost-effective%20to%20automate.%20Even%20a%20firm%20with%205%2C000%20employees%2C%20i.e.%2C%20larger%20than%2099.9%25%20of%20firms%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20could%20only%20cost-effectively%20automate%20less%20than%20one%20tenth%20of%20their%20existing%20vision%20labor%20at%20the%20current%20cost%20structure.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20agrees%20that%20the%20costs%20for%20AI%20will%20come%20down%20over%20time%2C%20but%20the%20authors%20believe%20not%20as%20rapidly%20as%20some%20others%20suggest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20would%20take%20quite%20a%20while%20before%20AI%20made%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20these%20kinds%20of%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20bad%20news%3A%20This%20is%20only%20a%20study%20for%20jobs%20that%20could%20be%20replaced%20by%20computer%20vision%2C%20which%20is%20a%20pretty%20specific%20thing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20I'm%20not%20so%20worried%20about%20%3Cem%3Ecomputer%20vision%3C%2Fem%3E%20taking%20over%20my%20job%20writing%20this%20article%2C%20but%20uh%20%E2%80%A6%20well%20%E2%80%A6%20you%20know.%20%F0%9F%98%AC%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-probably-will-not-take-your-job-just-yet-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705966342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aee23c43bb77284b9f8347%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-probably-will-not-take-your-job-just-yet-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20research%20paper%20shows%20that%20it's%20not%20really%20cost-effective%20to%20replace%20humans%20with%20computer%20vision.%20That's%20comforting%2C%20but%20who%20knows%20for%20how%20long%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-probably-will-not-take-your-job-just-yet-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NASA%20Spacecraft%20'Pings'%20India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20Lander%20On%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELaser%20instrument%20onboard%20a%20NASA%20spacecraft%20orbiting%20the%20Moon%20has%20successfully%20pinged%20the%20Vikram%20lander%20of%20India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%2C%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laser%20beam%20was%20transmitted%20and%20reflected%20between%20the%20Lunar%20Reconnaissance%20Orbiter%20(LRO)%20and%20an%20Oreo-sized%20device%20on%20Vikram%20lander%2C%20opening%20the%20door%20to%20a%20new%20style%20of%20precisely%20locating%20targets%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%2C%20NASA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20was%20100%20kilometers%20away%20from%20LRO%2C%20near%20Manzinus%20crater%20in%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole%20region%2C%20when%20LRO%20transmitted%20laser%20pulses%20toward%20it%20on%20December%2012%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20orbiter%20registered%20light%20that%20had%20bounced%20back%20from%20a%20tiny%20NASA%20retroreflector%20aboard%20Vikram%2C%20NASA%20scientists%20knew%20their%20technique%20had%20finally%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESending%20laser%20pulses%20towards%20an%20object%20and%20measuring%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20the%20light%20to%20bounce%20back%20is%20a%20commonly%20used%20way%20to%20track%20the%20locations%20of%20Earth-orbiting%20satellites%20from%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20using%20the%20technique%20in%20reverse%E2%80%94to%20send%20laser%20pulses%20from%20a%20moving%20spacecraft%20to%20a%20stationary%20one%20to%20determine%20its%20precise%20location%E2%80%94has%20many%20applications%20at%20the%20Moon%2C%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20showed%20that%20we%20can%20locate%20our%20retroreflector%20on%20the%20surface%20from%20the%20Moon's%20orbit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Xiaoli%20Sun%2C%20who%20led%20the%20team%20at%20NASA's%20Goddard%20Space%20Flight%20Center%2C%20that%20developed%20the%20retroreflector%20on%20Vikram%20as%20part%20of%20a%20partnership%20between%20NASA%20and%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organization%20(ISRO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20improve%20the%20technique%20so%20that%20it%20can%20become%20routine%20for%20missions%20that%20want%20to%20use%20these%20retroreflectors%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Sun%20said%20in%20a%20NASA%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%202%20inches%2C%20or%205%20centimeters%2C%20wide%2C%20NASA's%20tiny%20but%20mighty%20retroreflector%2C%20called%20a%20Laser%20Retroreflector%20Array%2C%20has%20eight%20quartz-corner-cube%20prisms%20set%20into%20a%20dome-shaped%20aluminum%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20is%20simple%20and%20durable%2C%20scientists%20say%2C%20requiring%20neither%20power%20nor%20maintenance%2C%20and%20can%20last%20for%20decades.%20Its%20configuration%20allows%20the%20retroreflector%20to%20reflect%20light%20coming%20in%20from%20any%20direction%20back%20to%20its%20source%2C%20NASA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetroreflectors%20can%20be%20used%20for%20many%20applications%20in%20science%20and%20exploration%20and%20have%20been%20in%20use%20at%20the%20Moon%20since%20the%20Apollo%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20reflecting%20light%20back%20to%20Earth%2C%20the%20suitcase-size%20retroreflectors%20revealed%20that%20the%20Moon%20is%20moving%20away%20from%20our%20planet%20at%20a%20rate%20of%203.8%20centimeters%20per%20year%2C%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20ISRO%20said%20the%20Laser%20Retroreflector%20Array%20(LRA)%20on%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20has%20begun%20serving%20as%20a%20fiducial%20point%20(precisely%20located%20markers%20for%20reference)%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNASA's%20Lunar%20Reconnaissance%20Orbiter%20(LRO)%20achieved%20a%20laser%20range%20measurement%20using%20the%20LRA%20by%20successfully%20detecting%20signals%20reflected%20by%20it%20on%20December%2012%2C%202023.%20The%20ranging%20utilized%20the%20Lunar%20Orbiter%20Laser%20Altimeter%20(LOLA)%20on%20the%20LRO.%20The%20observation%20occurred%20during%20lunar%20night%20time%2C%20with%20the%20LRO%20ascending%20to%20the%20east%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20space%20agency%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705966260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Famdhuusk_pragyan-rover-clicked-an-image-of-vikram-lander-twitter_625x300_30_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnasa-spacecraft-pings-indias-chandrayaan-3-lander-on-moon-4913940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Laser%20instrument%20onboard%20a%20NASA%20spacecraft%20orbiting%20the%20Moon%20has%20successfully%20pinged%20the%20Vikram%20lander%20of%20India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%2C%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnasa-spacecraft-pings-indias-chandrayaan-3-lander-on-moon-4913940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnasa-spacecraft-pings-indias-chandrayaan-3-lander-on-moon-4913940%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnasa-spacecraft-pings-indias-chandrayaan-3-lander-on-moon-4913940%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Horoscope%20Today%3A%20Read%20your%20daily%20astrological%20predictions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705966200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107063129%2Cimgsize-12824.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fastrology%2Fhoroscope%2Fhoroscope-today-january-23-2024-read-your-daily-astrological-predictions%2Farticleshow%2F107062962.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Read%20daily%20horoscope%20predictions%20for%20January%2023%2C%202024%3A%20Know%20all%20about%20the%20astrological%20events%20and%20influences%20that%20will%20be%20affecting%20each%20of%20the%2012%20zodiac