C%20where%20the%20company%20handcrafts%20all%20its%20products%20using%20only%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20leather%20sourced%20from%20around%20the%20world%20and%20everything%20else%20that%20goes%20into%20these%20beautiful%20cowboy%20boots.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20something%20exotic%2C%20like%20rattlesnake%20or%20caiman%20with%20lots%20of%20hand%20tooling%20and%20beautiful%20details%20and%20colors%2C%20look%20no%20further%20for%20some%20of%20the%20best%20cowboy%20boots%20money%20can%20buy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20if%20you're%20thinking%20of%20getting%20a%20pair%2C%20they'll%20run%20you%20around%20%24500%20on%20the%20low%20end%20and%20into%20the%20thousands%20on%20the%20high%20end.%20But%20considering%20all%20of%20Black%20Jack%20Boots'%20products%20are%20true%20works%20of%20art%20that%20have%20been%20meticulously%20crafted%20and%20will%20last%20for%20decades%20if%20properly%20cared%20for%2C%20they're%20a%20worthy%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrye%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Frye%20Company%20Duke%20Roper%20Boot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b0c4812dc4f001a1744a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFrye%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrye%20may%20be%20based%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20country%20from%20where%20cowboys%20originated%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20stop%20this%20heritage%20brand%20founded%20in%20Massachusetts%20in%201863%20from%20crafting%20some%20exceptional%20cowboy%20boots%20that%20are%20heavy%20on%20the%20rock%20n'%20roll%20vibes.%20The%20brand%20uses%20premium%20leathers%20in%20its%20Western-style%20boots%20including%20supple%20pull-up%20leather%20for%20the%20Duke%20Roper%2C%20and%20ostrich%20for%20the%20Bruce%20Pull%20On.%20Pull-up%20leather%20is%20made%20using%20aniline%20dyes%20that%20can't%20mask%20the%20hide's%20natural%20grain%20and%20thus%20require%20top-quality%20leather%20for%20the%20process.%20Frye%20also%20uses%20Goodyear%20welting%20so%20the%20boots%20can%20be%20easily%20resoled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Frye%20selections%20below%20are%20all%20lined%20in%20leather%20and%20made%20in%20Leon%2C%20Mexico%2C%20using%20traditional%20construction%20methods.%20While%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20materials%20and%20manufacturing%20means%20you%20get%20a%20great%20boot%2C%20like%20many%20high-end%20brands%2C%20you're%20also%20paying%20for%20the%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThursday%20Boot%20Co.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thursday%20Boot%20Co.%20Maverick%20Boot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b0ca7bf943d00195c6bb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThursday%20Boot%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20direct-to-consumer%20footwear%20brand%20Thursday%20Boot%20Co.%2C%20has%20been%20crafting%20exceptional%20boots%20at%20a%20fair%20price.%20While%20the%20company's%20better%20known%20for%20its%20dress%20boots%20and%20leather%20sneakers%2C%20Thursday%20Boot%20Co.%20also%20makes%20excellent%20cowboy%20boots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand's%20offerings%20include%20everything%20you'd%20expect%20from%20the%20best%20cowboy%20boots%2C%20like%20full-grain%20leather%20with%20hand-stitched%20patterning%2C%20stacked%20leather%20heels%2C%20and%20Goodyear%20welt%20construction.%20Plus%2C%20Thursday%20Boot%20Co.%20goes%20further%20by%20fully%20lining%20its%20boots%20in%20a%20buttery%20glove%20leather%20and%20including%20cork%20midsoles%20and%20shock-absorbing%20insoles%20for%20comfort.%20And%20they%20all%20come%20in%20at%20under%20%24250.%20The%20company's%20boots%20tend%20to%20run%20about%20a%20half-size%20larger%20than%20what%20you%20would%20wear%20in%20a%20sneaker%2C%20so%20consider%20sizing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%