arrow%20valleys%20may%20have%20magnified%20the%20effects%2C%20causing%20waves%20of%20over%2065%20feet%20to%20flood%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20written%20records%20of%20the%20disaster.%20Instead%2C%20the%20story%20is%20in%20the%20sediment%20deposits%20from%20lakes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuk-police-dyed-blue-lagoon-black-to-stop-people-visiting-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elagoons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20bodies%20of%20water%20that%20formed%20during%20the%20tsunami.%20The%20wave%20eroded%20sediment%20on%20land%20but%20also%20brought%20in%20more%20from%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20layers%20are%20distinctive%2C%20they%20often%20erode%20with%20time%20and%20human%20activity.%20However%2C%20they%20can%20give%20scientists%20clues%20about%20how%20far%20inland%20a%20wave%20traveled%20and%20how%20often%20similar%20events%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20a%20beach%20and%20water%20at%20Howick%2C%20Northumberland%20in%20England%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaffbcdcdb354a985963e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresent-day%20Howick%2C%20England%2C%20where%20a%20tsunami%20may%20have%20hit%20over%208%2C000%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3EMarc%20Guitard%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20the%20huge%20waves%20didn't%20reach%20Howick%20at%20all.%20The%20location%20has%20sediment%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20result%20of%20a%20sudden%20event.%20Yet%20it's%20coarser%20than%20the%20finer%20sand%20found%20elsewhere%20attributed%20to%20the%20Storegga%20waves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%20sedimentary%20research%20at%20Howick%20could%20accurately%20identify%20whether%20deposits%20were%20produced%20by%20the%20tsunami%20at%20this%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharrocks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20population%20unprepared%20for%20a%20tsunami%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETsunamis%20are%20rare%20in%20the%20British%20Isles.%20The%20Mesolithic%20population%20likely%20never%20experienced%20one%20before%20the%20Storegga%20landslide%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20speculate%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fitic.ioc-unesco.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereceding%20sea%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20precedes%20a%20giant%20wave%20may%20have%20drawn%20people%20to%20the%20water%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fepdf%2F10.1002%2Fjqs.3586%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eto%20collect%20stranded%20shellfish%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20happened%2C%20the%20tsunami%20could%20have%20drowned%20a%20significant%20percentage%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20destruction%20of%20resources%2C%20like%20hazel%20trees%2C%20could%20have%20also%20led%20to%20famine%20among%20survivors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumerical%20models%20%26quot%3Bcan%20reconstruct%20the%20Storegga%20tsunami%20but%20can%20never%20be%20fully%20representative%20of%20past%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharrocks%20said.%20The%20event%20was%20so%20long%20ago%20that%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20around%20the%20relative%20sea%20level%20position%2C%20topography%2C%20and%20elevation%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20researchers'%20models%2C%20only%20if%20the%20tsunami%20hit%20at%20high%20tide%20would%20it%20have%20affected%20Howick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20paper%20from%202021%2C%20researchers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffeart.2021.767460%2Ffull%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esuggested%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20tsunami%20may%20have%20destroyed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25-mesolithic-pits-found-in-bedfordshire-england-stun-archaeologists-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E