0any%20objection%20with%20Bangladesh%20about%20the%20activity%20of%20the%20research%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20government%20objected%20to%20the%20CSIS%20report%E2%80%99s%20conclusion%20that%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20research%20vessels%20had%20military%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20is%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20marine%20surveys%20are%20conducted%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20the%20UNCLOS%20and%20have%20contributed%20to%20research%20on%20ocean%20science.%20We%20hope%20relevant%20parties%20will%20view%20China%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20surveys%20as%20they%20are%20and%20not%20through%20tainted%20spectacles%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxwfw_665399%2Fs2510_665401%2F2511_665403%2F202401%2Ft20240112_11222952.html%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20on%20January%2012.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705945600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F29124657%2Fimage-949.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-strained-ties-with-india-chinese-research-vessel-en-route-to-maldives%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20the%20largest%20fleet%20of%20research%20vessels%20in%20the%20region%2C%20which%20experts%20believe%20serve%20both%20scientific%20and%20military%20purposes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-strained-ties-with-india-chinese-research-vessel-en-route-to-maldives%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20father%20fears%20hostage%20daughter%20was%20sexually%20abused%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705945341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F8F6F%2Fproduction%2F_132391763_mediaitem132391759.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3