ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68054411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joseph%20Boakai%2C%2079%2C%20is%20helped%20from%20the%20podium%20as%20the%20ceremony%20in%20the%20capital%20Monrovia%20is%20cut%20short.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68054411%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68054411.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68054411.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sena's%20Hindutva%20Roots%20in%20Clear%20Display%20As%20Uddhav%20Launches%20Poll%20Campaign%20from%20Nashik%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22220241%2FEffect-79.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Just%20two%20days%20before%20the%20BJP-led%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20idol%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20and%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20received%20an%20invite%20to%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20through%20a%20speed%20post.%20Despite%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20history%20associated%20with%20the%20contested%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20and%20Ayodhya%2C%20Thackeray%20stuck%20to%20his%20prior%20plan%20of%20visiting%20the%20Kalaram%20temple%20in%20Nashik%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20along%20with%20family%20and%20party%20workers%E2%80%94who%20have%20been%20camping%20in%20Nashik%20for%20a%20few%20days%E2%80%94first%20went%20to%20the%20memorial%20of%20Hindutva%20ideologue%20Vinayak%20Damodar%20Savarkar%20in%20Bhagur%20at%20Nashik%20and%20later%2C%20visited%20the%20Kalaram%20temple.%20The%20Thackeray%20family%2C%20all%20dressed%20in%20saffron%2C%20offered%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmaha%20arti%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revered%20temple%20has%20black-colour%20idols%20of%20Ram%2C%20Sita%2C%20and%20Lakshman.%20It%20is%20built%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Godavari%20River%20in%20the%20Panchvati%20area%20of%20Nashik.%20The%20epic%20story%20of%20Ram%20claims%20that%20while%20in%20exile%2C%20he%20along%20with%20Sita%20and%20Lakshman%20had%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20Panchvati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20had%20announced%20his%20visit%20to%20Kalaram%20temple%20on%20January%2011.%20This%20announcement%20acted%20as%20a%20prompt%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20visiting%20Maharashtra%20to%20launch%20multiple%20development%20projects.%20Modi%20made%20a%20quick%20visit%20to%20Kalaram%20temple%20and%20even%20%E2%80%9Cwiped%E2%80%9D%20the%20temple%20floor.%20Since%20Thackeray%20had%20not%20announced%20his%20plan%20to%20visit%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20memorial%20earlier%2C%20Modi%20missed%20out%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%E2%80%99s%20two-day%20visit%20to%20the%20historical%20town%20of%20Nashik%20is%20also%20a%20launch%20of%20his%20outfit%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%20After%20the%20Kalaram%20temple%20visit%2C%20Thackeray%20is%20scheduled%20to%20celebrate%20his%20father%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20Bal%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20birth%20anniversary%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20four%20years%20since%20Thackeray%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20BJP.%20In%20these%20years%2C%20the%20party%20has%20gone%20through%20both%20radical%20transformations%20and%20faced%20political%20blows.%20In%202019%2C%20Thackeray%20forged%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20and%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%20As%20a%20party%20with%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20MLAs%2C%20he%20also%20got%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Thackeray%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20working%20in%20sync%20with%20his%20Congress%20and%20NCP%2C%20there%20were%20several%20instances%20when%20Thackeray%20distanced%20himself%20from%20his%20allies.%20More%20specifically%2C%20at%20the%20time%20when%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20Hindutva%20was%20questioned.%20To%20recall%20one%20such%20instance%2C%20last%20year%20during%20the%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20took%20on%20Savarkar%2C%20Thackeray%20warned%20him%20against%20talking%20about%20his%20%E2%80%9CGod-like%20figure%E2%80%9D.%20Thackeray%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20said%2C%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20any%20insult%20hurled%20at%20Savarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20Thackeray%20faced%20a%20major%20jolt%20when%20a%20party%20confidante%20Eknath%20Shinde%20broke%20the%20party%2C%20taking%20away%20the%20majority%20of%20MLAs.%20Today%2C%20Shinde%20is%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20election%20commission%20and%20the%20state%20speaker%20have%20allotted%20his%20faction%20the%20party%20bow-and-arrow%20symbol.%20His%20faction%20has%20also%20been%20legitimised%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Creal%20Shiv%20Sena%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20has%20continued%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20and%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20united%20under%20the%20acronym%20INDIA%20or%20the%20Indian%20National%20Democratic%20Inclusive%20Alliance.%20But%20his%20stand%20is%20not%20necessarily%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20while%20has%20emerged%20as%20an%20anti-BJP%20face%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20he%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20foundation%20laid%20by%20his%20father%20Bal%20Thackeray%20in%20the%20state.%20Even%20today%2C%20at%20the%20Kalaram%20temple%2C%20Thackeray%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20choose%20social%20justice%20over%20communalism.%20He%20could%20have%20invoked%20the%201930s%20agitation%20led%20by%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20Sane%20Guruji%20at%20the%20very%20same%20Kalaram%20temple%2C%20one%20of%20the%20important%20temple-entry%20agitations%20of%20our%20times.%20Instead%2C%20Thackeray%20chose%20Savarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyodhya%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20ensuring%20Bal%20Thackeray%20remains%20both%20a%20relevant%20and%20powerful%20figure%20in%20Maharashtra.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20recall%20Bal%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%201992%20riots.%20Senior%20Thackeray%20was%20indicted%20by%20the%20Srikrishna%20Commission%20of%20inquiry%20for%20having%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20both%20flaring%20communal%20tension%20and%20provoking%20his%20party%20men%20to%20run%20amok%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20testimonies%20of%20riot%20victims%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20policemen%20point%20at%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%E2%80%99s%20active%20role%20in%20the%20riots%20that%20went%20on%20for%20many%20weeks%20between%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20and%20January%201993.%20The%20commission%E2%80%99s%20conservative%20estimate%20claimed%20that%20over%20900%20persons%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20were%20killed.%20Over%202%2C000%20were%20seriously%20injured%20in%20this%20violence.%20While%20many%20riot%20cases%20have%20ended%20up%20as%20dormant%20files%2C%20a%20few%20cases%20are%20still%20on%20trial%20in%20Mumbai%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20faction%20is%20in%20a%20precarious%20condition.%20Considering%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%20and%20corporators%20of%20major%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Nashik%20have%20switched%20to%20the%20Shinde%20faction%2C%20it%20is%20no%20less%20a%20herculean%20task%20for%20him%20to%20revive%20his%20party%20months%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20soon%20to%20follow%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705941948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20