ates%20and%20those%20not%20part%20of%20any%20religion%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20This%20nation%20belongs%20to%20all%20people%20and%20all%20sections%20of%20Indian%20society%20in%20equal%20measure.%20As%20those%20who%20have%20taken%20an%20oath%20to%20uphold%20the%20Constitution%2C%20we%20ought%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20person%20within%20our%20territories%20enjoys%20these%20rights.%20We%20cannot%20be%20promoting%20one%20religion%20above%20all%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijayan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20major%20departure%20from%20our%20times%20when%20our%20constitutional%20office%20bearers%20have%20been%20cautious%20from%20taking%20part%20in%20religious%20events%20as%20it%20would%20cast%20aspersions%20on%20our%20credentials%20as%20a%20secular%20state.%20Now%20we%20have%20come%20to%20a%20point%20in%20time%2C%20when%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20religious%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20the%20country%20is%20being%20celebrated%20as%20a%20state%20event.%20Most%20of%20us%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20rituals%20by%20the%20trust%20in%20charge%20of%20it.%20As%20those%20who%20have%20pledged%20to%20preserve%20and%20protect%20our%20constitution%2C%20let%20us%20reaffirm%20our%20commitment%20to%20its%20secular%20character%20by%20declining%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20event%20upholding%20our%20constitutional%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EComrade%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20on%20Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration..%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6CdsnilLXj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6CdsnilLXj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20CPI%20(M)%20(%40cpimspeak)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcpimspeak%2Fstatus%2F1749348072742854735%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20to%20fight%20the%20%E2%80%98anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%20image%20the%20BJP%20is%20building%20about%20him%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fwe-worship-mahatma-gandhis-ram-not-bjps-siddaramaiah-2859651%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20worship%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20not%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20was%20Raghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram.%20His%20last%20words%20were%20Hey%20Ram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20say%20Siddaramaiah%20is%20an%20atheist.%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20believer.%20I%20have%20Rama%20in%20my%20name.%20I%20am%20Siddarama.%20I%20am%20Siddaramaiah%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20opposed%20the%20existence%20of%20God.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20even%20chanted%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20and%20made%20the%20crowd%20say%20it%20aloud.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20slogan%20isn%E2%80%99t%20someone%E2%80%99s%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20nation%20worships%20Sri%20Ramachandra.%20In%20my%20village%2C%20I%20funded%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said%2C%20recalling%20how%20he%20used%20to%20participate%20in%20%3Cem%3Ebhajans%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20his%20village%20during%20%3Cem%3EDhanurmasa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20no%20God%20wants%20to%20be%20loved%20excessively.%20Basavanna%20said%20there%E2%80%99s%20God%20within%20us.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20he%20said%20that%20body%20is%20the%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20God%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20pleased%20if%20worship%20is%20%E2%80%98melodramatic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20said%20all%20religions%20want%20good%20for%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%2C%20including%20Gandhi%2C%20spoke%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%20It%20is%20what%20Kuvempu%20said%20%E2%80%93%20a%20garden%20of%20peace%20for%20all%20of%20humanity.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20Constitution%20speaks%20of%20co-existence%20and%20harmony.%20We%20must%20live%20with%20humanity%20without%20hating%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20is%20%E2%80%98anti-women%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(BJP)%20talk%20about%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20but%20what%20about%20Goddess%20Sita%3F%20She%20was%20all%20along%20with%20Lord%20Ram%20during%20his%20exile.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20speak%20about%20her%20as%20they%20are%20anti-women.%20We%20are%20worshippers%20of%20Goddess%20Durga%2C%20so%20they%20should%20not%20try%20to%20lecture%20us%20about%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20said%20at%20the%20all-faith%20rally%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20politicising%20religion%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20I%20am%20against%20such%20practice.%20I%20have%20no%20objection%20against%20those%20worshipping%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20but%20object%20to%20interference%20with%20the%20food%20habits%20of%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-anti-women-dig-at-bjp-they-talk-about-lord-ram-not-goddess-sita-101705929898953.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20had%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPran%20Pratishta%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20ceremony%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20our%20(politicians)%20job%20to%20do%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%20It%20is%20the%20job%20of%20the%20priests.%20Our%20job%20is%20to%20create%20infrastructure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20TMC%20chief%20clarified%20that%20the%20all-faith%20rally%20is%20not%20to%20counter%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20to%20counter%20anyone%20or%20protest%20anything.%20I%20have%20already%20said%20religion%20belongs%20to%20individuals%20but%20festivals%20are%20for%20all.%20On%20January%2022%2C%20I%20will%20first%20offer%20prayers%20to%20Maa%20Kali%20and%20then%20lead%20the%20rally.%20It%20will%20touch%20temples%2C%20mosques%2C%20gurdwaras%20and%20churches%20along%20its%20route%20before%20reaching%20Park%20Circus%20where%20a%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmalayalam-actors-directors-share-constitution-preamble-on-ram-temple-inauguration-day%5C%22%3EMalayalam%20Actors%2C%20Directors%20Share%20Constitution%20Preamble%20on%20Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20(IUML)%20state%20president%20Panakkad%20Syed%20Sadiq%20Ali%20Shihab%20Thangal%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20misusing%20Lord%20Ram%20for%20political%20gains%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fkerala%2F2024%2FJan%2F22%2Fbjp-using-lord-ram-for-political-gains-iuml%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IUML%20is%20not%20against%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20but%20the%20party%20is%20exposing%20the%20political%20game%20played%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Those%20who%20are%20ruling%20the%20party%20are%20spreading%20hatred%20and%20are%20using%20Ram%20temple%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thangal%20said%2C%20while%20inaugurating%20the%20Maha%20Rally%20organised%20by%20the%20Muslim%20Youth%20League%20in%20Kozhikode%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705940151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fw