%2C%20%26quot%3BDespite%20such%20insults%2C%20I%20have%20adjusted%20and%20attended%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20meetings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20being%20stopped%20in%20Assam%20from%20visiting%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Vaishnav%20saint%20Srimant%20Sankardeva%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20going%20to%20the%20temple%20isn't%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20highlighted%20her%20proactive%20stance%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20politicians%20today%20took%20on%20the%20BJP%20head-on%3F%20Somebody%20went%20to%20one%20temple%20and%20thought%20it%20was%20sufficient%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not.%20I%20am%20the%20only%20one%20who%20visited%20the%20temple%2C%20gurudwara%2C%20church%2C%20and%20mosque.%20I%20have%20been%20fighting%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20When%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20issue%20(demolition)%20happened%2C%20and%20violence%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20I%20was%20on%20the%20streets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20remarks%20came%20as%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20symbolic%20journey%20of%20religious%20harmony%2C%20leading%20an%20all-faith%20rally%20that%20included%20visits%20to%20diverse%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20such%20as%20a%20temple%2C%20mosque%2C%20church%2C%20and%20gurdwara%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI%20(M)-led%20Left%20Front%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20TMC%20collectively%20constitute%20the%2028-party%20strong%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc.%20However%2C%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%20and%20Congress%20have%20aligned%20against%20the%20TMC%20and%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20explicitly%20mentioning%20the%20Congress%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20criticised%20them%20for%20delaying%20seat-sharing%20discussions%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20power%20and%20mass%20base%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20fight%20against%20them.%20But%20some%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20us%20about%20seat%20sharing.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%2C%20then%20at%20least%20don't%20give%20away%20seats%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20comments%20followed%20her%20assertion%20during%20an%20internal%20party%20meeting%20three%20days%20ago%20that%20the%20TMC%20is%20prepared%20to%20independently%20contest%20all%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bengal%20if%20not%20given%20due%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFissures%20within%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%20have%20become%20evident%2C%20particularly%20between%20its%20key%20allies%2C%20Congress%20and%20TMC%2C%20regarding%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC's%20offer%20of%20two%20seats%20based%20on%20Congress's%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20victories%20was%20deemed%20insufficient%20by%20the%20grand-old%20party%2C%20escalating%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20coincided%20with%20state%20Congress%20president%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20a%20vocal%20TMC%20critic%2C%20asserting%20that%20his%20party%20wouldn't%20%26quot%3Bbeg%26quot%3B%20for%20seats%20from%20the%20TMC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20TMC%20secured%2022%20seats%2C%20Congress%20won%20two%2C%20and%20BJP%20secured%2018%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chowdhury%2C%20also%20the%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20won%20the%20Baharampur%20seat%2C%20while%20Abu%20Hasem%20Khan%20Choudhury%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20minister%2C%20secured%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20from%20Malda%20Dakshin%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20recently%20decided%20to%20abstain%20from%20an%20INDIA%20bloc%20virtual%20meeting%20and%20emphasised%20the%20necessity%20for%20Congress%20to%20recognise%20its%20limitation