de-quits-to-join-interglobe-enterprises-as-group-ceo-124012200869_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fudaan-cfo-aditya-pande-quits-to-join-interglobe-enterprises-as-group-ceo-124012200869_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Findings%20Of%20Cruelty%20Against%20Wife%20Can't%20Be%20Basis%20To%20Deny%20Maintenance%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20findings%20of%20cruelty%20against%20a%20wife%20in%20divorce%20proceedings%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20to%20deny%20her%20maintenance%20by%20husband%20under%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court's%20observation%20came%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20plea%20by%20a%20woman%20challenging%20a%20sessions%20court's%20order%20which%20had%20set%20aside%20a%20magisterial%20court's%20order%20directing%20her%2065-year-old%20estranged%20husband%20to%20pay%20her%20Rs%201%20lakh%20monthly%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sessions%20court%20had%20remanded%20it%20back%20to%20the%20magisterial%20court%20for%20adjudication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20in%20my%20considered%20view%2C%20the%20findings%20of%20cruelty%20against%20the%20wife%20in%20the%20divorce%20proceedings%2C%20by%20itself%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20to%20deny%20maintenance%20to%20the%20wife%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Amit%20Bansal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20placed%20reliance%20on%20several%20judgments%20passed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20which%20it%20was%20observed%20that%20even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20finding%20of%20cruelty%20against%20the%20wife%2C%20it%20cannot%20by%20itself%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20denying%20maintenance%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20bar%20of%20cruelty%20in%20the%20right%20of%20the%20wife%20to%20claim%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20held%20by%20the%20top%20court%20in%20one%20of%20the%20judgments%20that%20even%20if%20divorce%20has%20been%20granted%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20desertion%20by%20the%20wife%2C%20this%20cannot%20be%20a%20ground%20to%20deny%20maintenance%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20submission%20of%20the%20husband%20in%20which%20he%20relied%20on%20the%20findings%20in%20the%20judgement%20of%20divorce%20granted%20in%20his%20favour%20by%20the%20family%20court%20on%20grounds%20of%20cruelty%20and%20desertion%20by%20the%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20sessions%20court's%20order%20saying%20that%20instead%20of%20adjudicating%20and%20returning%20a%20finding%20on%20several%20issues%2C%20the%20appellate%20court%20simply%20remanded%20the%20matter%20back%20to%20the%20trial%20court%20without%20giving%20any%20reasons%20or%20justification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20order%20of%20remand%20is%20completely%20cryptic%20and%20without%20giving%20any%20reasons%20justifying%20the%20remand%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20sessions%20court's%20finding%20that%20the%20son%20had%20already%20attained%20the%20age%20of%20majority%20and%20thus%2C%20no%20relief%20could%20be%20granted%20to%20him%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20that%20the%20sessions%20court%20failed%20to%20take%20into%20account%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20granted%20maintenance%20from%202009%20to%202016%20and%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20this%20period%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20parties%2C%20even%20though%20he%20had%20attained%20the%20age%20of%20majority%2C%20was%20still%20pursuing%20his%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20obligation%20of%20a%20father%20towards%20his%20child%20does%20not%20end%20when%20the%20child%20attains%20majority%20even%20though%20he%20is%20still%20pursuing%20his%20studies%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20year%202009%20and%20almost%2014%20years%20have%20elapsed%20and%20the%20wife%20has%20not%20been%20granted%20any%20interim%20maintenance%20other%20than%20the%20sum%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20paid%20by%20the%20husband%20pursuant%20to%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20this%20court.%20Accordingly%2C%20even%20though%20I%20am%20remanding%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20appellate%20court%20to%20decide%20the%20appeal%20on%20merits%2C%20it%20is%20deemed%20appropriate%20that%20an%20amount%20of%20interim%20maintenance%20is%20fixed%20by%20this%20Court%20pending%20the%20adjudication%20of%20the%20appeal%20on%20merits%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Bansal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20asked%20the%20man%20to%20pay%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20the%20wife%20as%20interim%20maintenance%20from%20December%2016%2C%202009%20when%20the%20complaint%20under%20the%20DV%20Act%20was%20filed%20till%20November%201%2C%202019%20when%20the%20order%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20sessions%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sum%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20already%20paid%20by%20the%20man%20to%20the%20woman%20shall%20be%20deducted%20from%20the%20amount%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705935060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffindings-of-cruelty-against-wife-cant-be-basis-to-deny-maintenance-delhi-high-court-4911830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20findings%20of%20cruelty%20against%20a%20wife%20in%20divorce%20proceedings%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20to%20deny%20her%20maintenance%20by%20husband%20under%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffindings-of-cruelty-against-wife-cant-be-basis-to-deny-maintenance-delhi-high-court-4911830%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffindings-of-cruelty-against-wife-cant-be-basis-to-deny-maintenance-delhi-high-court-4911830%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffindings-of-cruelty-against-wife-cant-be-basis-to-deny-maintenance-delhi-high-court-4911830%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Zombie'%20Virus%20Frozen%20In%20Arctic%20Could%20Spark%20Deadly%20Pandemic%2C%20Say%20Scientists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20warned%20about%20the%20dangers%20posed%20by%20viruses%20buried%20under%20ice%20caps%20in%20the%20Arctic%20and%20other%20places.%20They%20have%20stated%20that%20the%20melting%20Arctic%20permafrost%20could%20release%20the%20'zombie%20viruses'%20and%20trigger%20a%20catastrophic%20global%20health%20emergency%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsociety%2F2024%2Fjan%2F21%2Farctic-zombie-viruses-in-siberia-could-spark-terrifying-new-pandemic-scientists-warn%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20threat%20has%20increased%20since%20rising%20temperatures%20due%20to%20global%20warming%20started%20melting%20the%20frozen%20ice.%20To%20better%20understand%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20these%20viruses%2C%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fscientists-revive-zombie-virus-which-spent-48-500-years-frozen-in-arctic-3850163%5C%22%3E%20scientist%20revived%20some%20of%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20samples%20taken%20from%20Siberian%20permafrost%20last%20year.%20These%20viruses%20have%20spent%20thousands%20of%20years%20frozen%20in%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneticist%20Jean-Michel%20Claverie%20of%20Aix-Marseille%20University%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20analyses%20of%20pandemic%20threats%20focus%20on%20diseases%20that%20might%20emerge%20in%20southern%20regions%20and%20then%20spread%20north.%20By%20contrast%2C%20little%20attention%20has%20been%20given%20to%20an%20outbreak%20that%20might%20emerge%20in%20the%20far%20north%20and%20then%20travel%20south%20-%20and%20that%20is%20an%20oversight%2C%20I%20believe.%20There%20are%20viruses%20up%20there%20that%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20infect%20humans%20and%20start%20a%20new%20disease%20outbreak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20scientist%20Marion%20Koopmans%20of%20the%20Erasmus%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Rotterdam%20agreed%20with%20the%20same%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20what%20viruses%20are%20lying%20out%20there%20in%20the%20permafrost%20but%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20real%20risk%20that%20there%20might%20be%20one%20capable%20of%20triggering%20a%20disease%20outbreak%20-%20say%20of%20an%20ancient%20form%20of%20polio.%20We%20have%20to%20assume%20that%20something%20like%20this%20could%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20buried%20in%20permafrost%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20live%20viruses%20could%20still%20infect%20single-celled%20creatures%2C%20as%20demonstrated%20by%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%20led%20by%20Claverie%20in%20Siberia%20in%202014.%20Additional%20investigation%2C%20which%20was%20published%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20identified%20several%20virus%20strains%20from%20seven%20distinct%20Siberian%20locations%20and%20demonstrated%20their%20ability%20to%20infect%20cultured%20cells.%20A%20virus%20sample%20dated%20back%2048%2C500%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20viruses%20we%20isolated%20were%20only%20able%20to%20infect%20amoebae%20and%20posed%20no%20risk%20to%20humans.%20However%2C%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20other%20viruses%20-%20currently%20frozen%20in%20the%20permafrost%20-%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20trigger%20illnesses%20in%20humans.%20We%20have%20identified%20genomic%20traces%20of%20poxviruses%20and%20herpesviruses%2C%20which%20are%20well-known%20human%20pathogens%2C%20for%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Claverie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%20is%20covered%20in%20permafrost%2C%20which%20has%20long%20supported%20the%20Arctic%20tundra%20and%20boreal%20forests%20of%20Alaska%2C%20Canada%20and%20Russia.%20Together%20with%20ancient%20viruses%2C%20it%20acts%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20time%20capsule%2C%20preserving%20the%20mummified%20remains%20of%20several%20extinct%20creatures.%20The%20region%20is%20heating%20up%20several%20times%20faster%20than%20the%20average%20rate%20of%20increase%20in%20global%20warming%2C%20according%20to%20meteorologists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20danger%20comes%20from%20another%20global%20warming%20impact%3A%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Arctic%20sea%20ice.%20That%20is%20allowing%20increases%20in%20shipping%2C%20traffic%20and%20industrial%20development%20in%20Siberia.%20Huge%20mining%20operations%20are%20being%20planned%2C%20and%20are%20going%20to%20drive%20vast%20holes%20into%20the%20deep%20permafrost%20to%20extract%20oil%20and%20ores.%20Those%20operations%20will%20release%20vast%20amounts%20of%20pathogens%20that%20still%20thrive%20there.%20Miners%20will%20walk%20in%20and%20breathe%20the%20viruses.%20The%20effects%20could%20be%20calamitous%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705934400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fqntbhilo_zombie-virus_625x300_10_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzombie-virus-which-spent-48-500-years-frozen-in-arctic-could-spark-deadly-pandemic-warn-scientists-4911838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20scientists%20stated%20that%20the%20melting%20Arctic%20permafrost%20could%20release%20the%20'zombie%20viruses'%20and%20trigger%20a%20catastrophic%20global%20health%20emergency%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl