aid%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20consecration%20%E2%80%9Cmakes%20it%20clear%20that%20Hindutva%20will%20be%20%5Bat%20the%5D%20front%20and%20centre%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022%20organisations%20added%20that%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20came%20amid%20increasing%20discrimination%20against%20India%E2%80%99s%20religious%20minorities%20and%20what%20they%20said%20were%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20rewrite%20history%20and%20present%20Muslims%20as%20having%20no%20ties%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20they%20said%20that%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%20were%20%E2%80%98appropriating%E2%80%99%20Muslim%20religious%20sites%20and%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-judgment%5C%22%3E2019%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20handing%20over%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20which%20stood%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20was%20demolished%20by%20Hindu%20nationalists%20in%201992%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20temple%20side%20gave%20rise%20to%20similar%20claims%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20Muslim%20places%20of%20worship%E2%80%9D%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20plaintiffs%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20in%20Mathura%20were%20built%20atop%20Hindu%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20India%20prepares%20for%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election%2C%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20%E2%80%93%20on%20land%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20mosque%20once%20stood%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20potent%20symbol%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20disregard%20for%20the%20right%20to%20exist%20for%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20public%20sphere%2C%20and%20to%20exert%20their%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20belief%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20joint%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20cements%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%20already%20set%20in%20motion%2C%20further%20appropriating%20minorities%E2%80%99%20cultural%20and%20religious%20heritage%2C%20and%20taking%20away%20their%20rights%20as%20Indian%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20also%20criticised%20the%20Ram%20Temple%E2%80%99s%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20saying%20it%20politicised%20a%20religious%20event%20and%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20active%20role%20in%20inaugurating%20the%20temple%20could%20mean%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modi-in-ram-temple-pran-prathishtha-end-of-secularism-as-distance-between-state-and-religion%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cprincipled%20distance%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20state%20and%20religion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20as%20set%20out%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20foundation%20as%20a%20secular%20nation%20%E2%80%93%20is%20obfuscated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20statement%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoint%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E22nd%20January%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20sets%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%20for%20minorities%20in%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20the%20undersigned%20diaspora%20organisations%20are%20extremely%20concerned%20about%20the%20dangerous%20precedent%20set%20by%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20to%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20general%20elections%2C%20taking%20place%20in%20April%20%E2%80%93%20May%202024.%20This%20is%20clearly%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign.%20Taking%20place%20four%20days%20before%20Republic%20Day%2C%20it%20is%20also%20an%20attempt%20to%20sideline%20and%20replace%20India%E2%80%99s%20secular%20Constitution%20which%20was%20drafted%20by%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20been%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%2016th%20century%20Babri%20Masjid%20Mosque%2C%20destroyed%20by%20Hindu%20supremacists%20in%201992.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-agrees-muslims-were-wronged-but-allows-ram-temple%2Farticle61621466.ece%5C%22%3Eruled%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favour%20of%20Hindu%20supremacists%E2%80%99%20claim%20to%20the%20land%20to%20authorize%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20despite%20deeming%20the%20destruction%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20Mosque%20as%20a%20criminal%20act.%20The%20ruling%20did%20not%20go%20as%20far%20as%20to%20condemn%20the%20cultural%20erasure%20of%20a%20historic%20Muslim%20site%2C%20however%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20seek%20to%20address%20the%20subsequent%20violent%20communal%20clashes%20in%20the%20country%20arising%20from%20its%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20planned%20%E2%80%98consecration%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20party%20and%20RSS%20stalwarts%20is%20a%20signal%20that%20India%20has%20moved%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20implementing%20the%20long-term%20RSS%20goals%20of%20making%20India%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20(State)%20and%20replacing%20the%20Constitution%20with%20the%20Manusmriti%2C%20a%20violently%20Brahminical%2C%20anti-Dalit%20and%20patriarchal%20ancient%20Hindu%20text.%20It%20also%2C%20of%20course%2C%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20Hindutva%20will%20be%20front%20and%20centre%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20happening%20against%20a%20backdrop%20of%20a%20horrifying%20escalation%20in%20discrimination%20and%20violence%20against%20religious%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%2C%20and%20is%20against%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%20the%20country%20and%20its%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20party%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20has%20been%20actively%20seeking%20to%20erase%20traces%20of%20Muslim%20heritage%20in%20India%2C%20for%20example%2C%20through%20the%20revision%20of%20school%20textbooks%20and%20by%20rewriting%20history%20as%20told%20in%20popular%20media%2C%20and%20in%20public%20and%20political%20spheres.%20This%20is%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20present%20the%20minority%20community%20as%20alien%20and%20the%20Other%2C%20without%20any%20ties%20to%20India%20as%20construed%20by%20Hindu%20supremacist%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appropriation%20of%20Muslim%20religious%20sites%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20Mosque%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20tools%20in%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20arsenal.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20on%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20Mosque%20in%202019%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-mathura-varanasi-why-the-coming-week-is-crucial-for-the-hindutva-project%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20well-planned%20campaigns%20by%20Hindu%20supremacists%20against%20Muslim%20places%20of%20worship%20elsewhere%20in%20India.%20In%20Mathura%20city%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20lawsuit%20is%20pending%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20location%20of%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20mosque%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Hindu%20God%20Krishna.%20In%20Varanasi%2C%20also%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Gyanwapi%20mosque%20is%20similarly%20being%20claimed%20by%20Hindu%20groups%20aligned%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20party.%20By%20entertaining%20legal%20claims%20to%20these%20historical%20mosques%2C%20courts%20including%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20have%20enabled%20these%20acts%20of%20appropriation.%20India%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20itself%20opened%20the%20doors%20to%20legal%20challenges%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-the-places-of-worship-act-must-be-preserved%5C%22%3EPlaces%20of%20Worship%20Act%201992%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20protect%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20historical%20buildings%20after%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20Mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20prepares%20for%20the%20upcoming%20General%20Election%2C%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20%E2%80%93%20on%20land%20where%20the%20Babri%20Majid%20mosque%20once%20stood%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20potent%20symbol%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20disregard%20for%20the%20right%20to%20exist%20for%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20public%20sphere%2C%20and%20to%20exert%20their%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20belief.%20It%20also%20cements%20a%20dangerous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fhistory%2Fhindu-mahasabha-ayodhya-madhya-pradesh-kamal-maula-mosque%5C%22%3Eprecedent%3C%2Fa%3E%20already%20set%20in%20motion%2C%20further%20appropriating%20minorities%E2%80%99%20cultural%20and%20religious%20heritage%2C%20and%20taking%20away%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fhistory%2Fhindu-mahasabha-ayodhya-madhya-pradesh-kamal-maula-mosque%5C%22%3Erights%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Indian%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESignatories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Asia%20Justice%20Campaign%3Cbr%3E%5CnSouth%20Asia%20Solidarity%20Group%3Cbr%3E%5CnAlliance%20Against%20Islamophobia%20.%20Australia%3Cbr%3E%5CnCoalition%20Against%20Fascism%20in%20India%3Cbr%3E%5CnCraigieburn%20Masjid%20and%20Community%20Centre%3Cbr%3E%5CnHindus%20for%20Human%20Rights%20%E2%80%93%20UK%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20Civil%20Watch%20International%2C%20North%20America%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20Labour%20Solidarity%20(UK)%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndian%20Alliance%20Paris%2C%20France%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndian%20American%20Muslim%20Council%3Cbr%3E%5CnInternational%20Solidarity%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%20in%20India%20(InSAF%20India)%3Cbr%3E%5CnMelbourne%20Grand%20Mosque%3Cbr%3E%5CnMuslim%20Collective%2C%20Australia%3Cbr%3E%5CnPeace%20in%20India%20(UK)%3Cbr%3E%5CnPeriyar%20Ambedkar%20Thoughts%20Circle%20of%20Australia.%20(PATCA).%20Australia%3Cbr%3E%5Cn