bals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmp-right-wing-activists-plant-saffron-flag-on-the-holy-cross-on-the-eve-of-ram-temple-ceremony%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Will%20Replace%20Kohli%20In%20IND%20Squad%20For%201st%202%20Tests%20vs%20ENG%3F%20Report%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20batting%20mainstay%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20against%20England%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons%20which%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20his%20presence%20and%20undivided%20attention%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BCCI%20said%20on%20Monday.%20The%20BCCI%20urged%20the%20fans%20and%20media%20to%20refrain%20from%20speculating%20about%20the%20exact%20reason%20for%20his%20forced%20break%20before%20the%20five-match%20series%20begins%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20January%2025.%20The%20Board%20said%20it%20will%20name%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20star%20batter%20soon.%20%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20has%20requested%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20to%20be%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20upcoming%20IDFC%20First%20Bank%20Test%20series%20against%20England%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20also%20said%20that%20Kohli%20has%20discussed%20his%20decision%20with%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20the%20team%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20has%20spoken%20to%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20team%20management%20and%20the%20selectors%20and%20has%20emphasized%20that%20while%20representing%20the%20country%20has%20always%20been%20his%20top%20priority%2C%20certain%20personal%20situations%20demand%20his%20presence%20and%20undivided%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20further%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20said%20that%20BCCI%20completely%20backs%20its%20star%20player%20and%20has%20faith%20in%20the%20team%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20get%20results%20even%20without%20its%20best%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20respects%20his%20decision%20and%20the%20Board%20and%20team%20management%20has%20extended%20its%20support%20to%20the%20star%20batter%20and%20is%20confident%20in%20the%20abilities%20of%20the%20remaining%20squad%20members%20to%20step%20up%20and%20deliver%20commendable%20performances%20in%20the%20Test%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20urged%20everyone%20to%20respect%20Kohli's%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20requests%20the%20media%20and%20fans%20to%20respect%20Virat%20Kohli's%20privacy%20during%20this%20time%20and%20refrain%20from%20speculating%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20personal%20reasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20focus%20should%20remain%20on%20supporting%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20as%20they%20embark%20on%20the%20upcoming%20challenges%20in%20the%20Test%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20learnt%20that%20both%20Shah%20and%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20were%20kept%20in%20loop%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20Kohli%20needing%20a%20break%20at%20some%20point%20during%20the%20England%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Kohli%20also%20skipped%20the%20first%20T20I%20game%20against%20Afghanistan%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20reasons%26quot%3B.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20had%20taken%20a%20short%20break%2C%20again%20for%20personal%20reasons%2C%20during%20India's%20tour%20of%20South%20Africa%20where%20he%20missed%20an%20intra-squad%20practice%20game%20and%20flew%20to%20London%2C%20within%20days%20after%20arriving%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20he%20took%20a%20break%2C%20which%20was%20not%20linked%20to%20any%20injury%2C%20during%20a%20Test%20series%20was%20a%20paternity%20leave%20in%202021%20when%20his%20daughter%20Vamika%20was%20born.%20He%20only%20played%20the%20first%20Test%20of%20that%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajat%20Patidar%20vs%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20as%20replacement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20understood%20that%20one%20among%20the%20two%20heavyweight%20India%20'A'%20performers%20--%20Rajat%20Patidar%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20of%20Mumbai%20--%20are%20frontrunners%20to%20replace%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatidar%20recently%20scored%20151%20against%20the%20England%20Lions%20in%20an%20unofficial%20Test%20and%20Sarfaraz%20scored%20a%20half-ton%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20same%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20talk%20of%20including%20veteran%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20in%20the%20line-up%20considering%20his%20experience%20of%2020%2C000%20plus%20first-class%20runs%2C%20including%207000%20in%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20if%20the%20current%20selection%20committee%20under%20Agarkar%20is%20ready%20to%20look%20back%20or%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20batting%20line-up%20for%20first%20Test%20will%20comprise%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20and%20KS%20Bharat%20(wk).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705931160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fv6ekhjig_virat-kohli-test-pc-bcci_625x300_15_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fwho-will-replace-virat-kohli-in-india-squad-for-first-two-tests-against-england-report-says-4910514%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20has%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20against%20England%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons%20which%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20his%20presence%20and%20undivided%2