r-sale-to-reduce-govt-s-stake-124012200754_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20shown%20preference%20for%20the%20OFS%20route%20to%20avoid%20dilution%20of%20its%20equity%20capital%20base%20while%20increasing%20the%20public%20float%20of%20shares%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-of-india-plans-offer-for-sale-to-reduce-govt-s-stake-124012200754_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-of-india-plans-offer-for-sale-to-reduce-govt-s-stake-124012200754_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-of-india-plans-offer-for-sale-to-reduce-govt-s-stake-124012200754_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Safe%20Is%20It%20To%20Travel%20By%20Air%3F%20What%20Experts%20Have%20To%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20a%20series%20of%20mid-air%20incidents%20have%20brought%20into%20focus%20the%20issue%20of%20air%20safety.%20The%20door%20of%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20Boeing%20plane%20that%20blew%20out%20mid-air%20prompted%20strong%20reactions%20from%20social%20media%20users%20and%20led%20to%20audit%20of%20Boeing%20products%20in%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20India.%20A%20few%20days%20before%20that%2C%20a%20Japan%20Airlines%20(JAL)%20Airbus%20collided%20with%20a%20smaller%20coastguard%20plane%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20Airbus%20catching%20fire.%20So%2C%20is%20it%20really%20safe%20to%20travel%20by%20air%3F%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20statistics%20and%20what%20the%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20Harvard%20University%20say%20that%20odds%20of%20being%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%20are%20one%20in%201.2%20million%2C%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20dying%20in%20such%20an%20incident%2C%20the%20odds%20increase%20to%20one%20in%2011%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20significantly%20lower%20than%20dying%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20-%20one%20in%205%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20any%20form%20of%20transport%20always%20safe%3F%20No%2C%20but%20if%20you%20choose%20not%20to%20fly%20and%20instead%20take%20a%20car%2C%20that's%20a%20far%20more%20dangerous%20way%20of%20travelling%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Aboulafia%2C%20aviation%20industry%20analyst%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Washington-based%20AeroDynamic%20Advisory%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F13%2Fis-air-travel-the-safest-mode-of-transportation%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl-Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20safety%20has%20increased%20over%20the%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20International%20Civil%20Aviation%20Organization%20(ICAO)%20releases%20its%20global%20safety%20report%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20in%202022%2C%20the%20aviation%20industry%20saw%20a%20nearly%2010%20per%20cent%20decrease%20in%20accidents%20compared%20to%202020.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20fatalities%20resulting%20from%20aircraft%20accidents%20dropped%20by%20over%2065%20per%20cent%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20study%20by%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%20showed%20there%20was%20only%20one%20fatality%20every%207.9%20million%20passengers%20who%20boarded%20the%20flights%20between%202008%20and%202017.%20The%20same%20stood%20at%20closer%20to%20one%20death%20per%202.7%20million%20passengers%20between%201998%20and%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MIT%20paper%20also%20presented%20decadal%20comparisons%20of%20in%20pre-9%2F11%20era%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20one%20fatality%20for%20every%201.3%20million%20passengers%20from%201988%20to%201997%2C%20which%20decreased%20to%20one%20per%20750%2C000%20boardings%20in%20the%20data%20from%201978%20to%201987.%20A%20decade%20before%20that%2C%20there%20was%20one%20fatality%20for%20every%20350%2C000%20passengers.%20Adjusted%20to%202023%20traffic%20figures%2C%20that%20would%20account%20for%20at%20least%2018%20aviation-related%20deaths%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20reason%20that%20has%20made%20air%20travel%20safer%20today%20is%20technological%20advancements%2C%20ranging%20from%20engineering%20overhauls%20to%20improved%20regulation.%20These%20include%20modern%20glass%20cockpits%2C%20improved%20jet%20engines%20and%20better%20equipment%20for%20flight%20crew%2C%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20and%20dispatchers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20work%20in%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20aircraft%20safety%20checks%20are%20carried%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20an%20aircraft%20is%20cleared%20for%20flying%2C%20regular%20maintenance%20checks%20called%20A%2C%20C%20and%20D%20checks%20are%20carried%20out%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EAl-Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E.%20An%20A%20check%20includes%20changing%20filters%2C%20lubricating%20key%20systems%20and%20inspecting%20emergency%20equipment%20followed%20by%20a%20teardown%20and%20detailed%20inspection%20of%20the%20aircraft%20under%20D-check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20airlines%20are%20able%20to%20do%20A%20checks%2C%20only%20certain%20airlines%20are%20able%20to%20do%20C%20or%20D%20checks%20themselves%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%20These%20checks%20are%20carried%20out%20at%20regular%20intervals%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20years%20an%20aircraft%20has%20been%20in%20service%20or%20its%20number%20of%20flight%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20so%20many%20checks%20and%20stringent%20safety%20protocols%2C%20what%20happened%20this%20month%20has%20left%20experts%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELondon-based%20independent%20aviation%20expert%20John%20Strickland%20told%20Al-Jazeera%20that%20the%20panel%20which%20flew%20off%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20secure%20part%20of%20the%20aircraft's%20structure.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20it's%20more%20surprising%20and%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20that%20this%20blowout%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aviation%20expert%20and%20consultant%20Alex%20Macheras%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BThis%20should%20not%20be%20downplayed%2C%20that's%20for%20sure.%20Because%20in%20modern%20commercial%20aviation%2C%20we%20do%20not%20see%20sections%20of%20an%20aircraft%20body%2C%20of%20fuselage%2C%20becoming%20separated%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20certainly%20not%20mid-flight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20Reading%20University%20has%20warned%20that%20safety%20issues%20will%20crop%20up%20due%20to%20air%20turbulences%2C%20which%20have%20increased%20by%2055%20percent%20over%20the%20North%20Atlantic%20between%201979%20and%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20concluded%20that%20turbulence%20will%20become%20worse%20with%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705929900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fp207jlco_alaska-airlines-flight-1282-mishap-reuters_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhow-safe-is-it-to-travel-by-air-what-experts-have-to-say-4911420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK's%20Reading%20University%20has%20warned%20that%20safety%20issues%20will%20crop%20up%20due%20to%20air%20turbulences%2C%20which%20have%20increased%20by%2055%20percent%20over%20the%20North%20Atlantic%20between%201979%20and%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhow-safe-is-it-to-travel-by-air-what-experts-have-to-say-4911420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhow-safe-is-it-to-travel-by-air-what-experts-have-to-say-4911420%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhow-safe-is-it-to-travel-by-air-what-experts-have-to-say-4911420%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Gets%20Double%20Lung%20Transplant%20After%20Years%20Of%20Vaping%3A%20%26quot%3BHad%201%25%20Chance%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2022-year-old%20man%20in%20the%20United%20States%20underwent%20a%20double%20lung%20transplant%20after%20he%20had%20only%20%26quot%3Bone%20per%20cent%20chance%20of%20survival%26quot%3B%20following%20years%20of%20heavy%20vaping%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F21%2Fnews%2Fnorth-dakota-man-jackson-allard-needs-double-lung-transplant-after-years-of-vaping%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jackson%20Allard%20from%20North%20Dakota%20was%20hospitalised%20and%20put%20on%20life%20support%20as%20his%20oxygen%20levels%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20clinic%20after%20complaining%20about%20stomach%20aches%20and%20low%20oxygen%20levels.%20He%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Influenza%204%20and%20double%20pneumonia.%20However%2C%20his%20condition%20worsened%20and%20he%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota.%20Mr%20Allard's%20health%20continued%20to%20decline%20and%20doctors%20decided%20to%20put%20him%20on%20life%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Allard's%20grandmother%20Doreen%20Hurlbur%20stated%20that%20her%20grandson%20developed%20these%20problems%20from%20vaping%20and%20it%20got%20so%20bad%20at%20a%20point%20that%20his%20heart%20stopped%20beating.%20She%20spoke%20to%20Valley%20News%20Live%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20doctor%20said%20he%20had%20a%20%C2%A0one%20per%20cent%20chance%20of%20living%20and%20we%20said%2C%20'He's%20fighting'.%20He's%20fought%20for%20how%20many%20weeks%20we're%20going%20to%20give%20him%20a%20chance%20to%20fight%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20any%20procedures%20or%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20also%20requested%20him%20to%20quit%20vaping%20as%20it%20can%20prove%20more%20dangerous%20than%20traditional%20smoking%20methods.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20stop%20vaping%2C%20and%20we%20kept%20telling%20him%20that%20over%20and%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20and%20he%20was%20a%20heavy%20vaper.%20He%20vaped%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Hurlburt%20said.%20However%2C%20her%20grandson%20kept%20on%20asserting%20that%20vaping%20is%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20than%20cigarettes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20grandmother%20thought%20she%20would%20lose%20her%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%2C%20outgoing%2C%20energetic%20and%20fun%26quot%3B%20grandson.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20for%20sure%20we%20were%20going%20to%20lose%20him.%20I%20thought%20for%20sure%20he's%20not%20going%20to%20survive%20this%2C%20but%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20kept%20picturing%20him%20coming%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022-year-old%20received%20a%20double%20lung%20transplant%20on%20January%201.%20He%20will%20have%20to%20undergo%20regular%20checkups%20for%20the%20next%20six%20months.%20Mr%20Allard%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20smoke%20or%20drink%20again.%20He%20will%20also%20need%20another%20transplant%20later.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705929840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F32l7ggug_vaping_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-22-gets-double-lung-transplant-after-years-of-heavy-vaping-had-1-chance-of-survival-4911414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Allard%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20smoke%20or%20drink%20again.%20He%20will%20also%20need%20another%20transplant%20later.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-22-gets-double-lung-transplant-after-years-of-heavy-vaping-had-1-chance-of-survival-4911414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-22-gets-double-lung-transplant-afte