he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20the%20(Assam)%20government%20and%20Modi%20ji%20will%20decide%20when%20and%20who%20can%20visit%20a%20mandir%20and%20when%20they%20cannot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20convoy%20was%20stopped%2C%20Gandhi%20sat%20down%20on%20the%20road%2C%20along%20with%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20supporters%2C%20who%20sang%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERaghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2010%20am%2C%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Kaliabor%2C%20along%20with%20MLA%20Sibamoni%20Bora%2C%20visited%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20representative%20of%20Rahul%20ji%2C%20I%20and%20the%20MLA%20went%20to%20the%20temple.%20All%20the%20priests%20said%20that%20their%20blessings%20are%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20We%20told%20the%20priests%20that%20Rahul%20ji%20wanted%20to%20come%20himself%20but%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20government%20was%20already%20organising%20some%20programme%20here%20and%20there%20could%20be%20some%20law%20and%20order%20issues.%20But%20when%20we%20went%20there%2C%20until%2010%20am%20no%20cultural%20programme%20was%20going%20on%20there.%20There%20was%20no%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20neither%20was%20there%20any%20crowd.%20This%20was%20a%20lie%20spread%20by%20the%20administration%20whose%20orders%20came%20directly%20from%20the%20chief%20minister.%20This%20is%20a%20black%20mark%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Batadrava%20Than%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20behalf%20of%20Shri%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20I%20visited%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Saint%20Srimanta%20Sankardeva.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20denied%20permission%20to%20visit%20Batadrava%20Than%20by%20the%20police%20citing%20law%26amp%3Border%20and%20pre%20scheduled%20program.%20The%20fact%20is%20the%20opposite%20because%20there%20was%20no%20program%20taking%20place.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzcF30bMhD4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzcF30bMhD4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20(%40GauravGogoiAsm)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGauravGogoiAsm%2Fstatus%2F1749297916894965985%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175517%2Fimage-1780.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221111%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175517%2Fimage-1780.png%201111w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175517%2Fimage-1780-300x173.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175517%2Fimage-1780-1024x591.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20along%20with%20MLA%20Sibamoni%20Bora%2C%20at%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Saint%20Srimanta%20Sankardeva%2C%20in%20Assam%2C%20on%20January%2022.%20Photo%3A%20X%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20and%20media%20in-charge%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20later%20in%20the%20day%20that%20it%20has%20always%20been%20the%20Assam%20government%E2%80%99s%20effort%20to%20prevent%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20from%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20participated%2C%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAhankaracharya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20may%20not%20want%20want%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20to%20go%20anywhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20media%20channels%20are%20focusing%20on%20only%20one%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EAhakaracharya%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20our%20country%20does%20not%20want%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20to%20go%20elsewhere%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20took%20this%20decision.%20We%20sat%20there%20near%20the%20barricades%20for%20close%20to%20two%20hours%20and%20met%20different%20people%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20who%20sat%20and%20sang%20bhajans.%20We%20only%20left%20after%20Gogoi%20and%20Bora%20returned%20from%20the%20Than.%20We%20could%20not%20follow%20our%20yatra%E2%80%99s%20programme%20today%20because%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20did%20not%20get%20permission%2C%20and%20I%20apologise%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20not%20a%20last-minute%20decision.%20There%20was%20no%20political%20or%20electoral%20objective%20behind%20this.%20That%20is%20why%20from%20January%2011%20we%20had%20decided%20that%20on%20January%2022%2C%20Rahul%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20visit%20the%20temple.%20We%20even%20said%20that%20only%20he%20will%20visit%20and%20no%20one%20else%2C%20in%20a%20police%20vehicle%20but%20they%20did%20not%20want%20him%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yatra%2C%20in%20its%20ninth%20day%2C%20later%20resumed%20at%202%20pm%20and%20proceeded%20towards%20Morigaon%20before%20heading%20to%20Nongpoh%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20(January%2021)%2C%20Sarma%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20had%20urged%20Gandhi%20to%20visit%20the%20Batadrava%20Than%20after%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20like%20there%20is%20a%20competition%20between%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20Batadrava%20Than.%20That%20is%20not%20good%20for%20Assam.%20So%2C%20we%20request%20that%20we%20would%20like%20it%20if%20he%20goes%20to%20Batadrava%20Than%20after%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20programme%20is%20done.%20I%20would%20like%20that.%20Otherwise%20television%20channels%20will%20show%20the%20two%20in%20a%20two-window.%20But%20that%20two-window%20will%20go%20against%20the%20image%20of%20Assam.%20There%20is%20no%20competition%20and%20he%20should%20not%20come%20and%20create%20that%20competition.%20That%20will%20be%20sad%20for%20people%20of%20Assam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20supporters%20with%20saffron%20flags%20surrounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-rahul-gandhi-meets-protestors-blows-kisses-to-bjp-supporters-raising-slogans%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20convoy%20and%20raised%20slogans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20allegedly%20attacked%20Assam%20Congress%20chief%20Bhupen%20Borah%20as%20well%20as%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%9C%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20'%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE'%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8C%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20BJP%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A1%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A5%A4%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AC%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%82%E