%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22L.K.%20Advani%2C%20Who%20Led%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Movement%2C%20Skips%20Temple%20Consecration%20Citing%20Extreme%20Cold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EVeteran%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20and%20former%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20L.K.%20Advani%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20citing%20the%20extreme%20cold%20conditions%20in%20north%20India.%20Advani%20led%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20and%20his%20%3Cem%3Erath%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20culminated%20in%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%20is%20now%2096.%20The%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20had%20reportedly%20told%20him%20and%20his%20colleague%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%20However%2C%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvishwa-hindu-parishad-advani-mm-joshi-to-ayodhya-ram-mandir-event-after-temple-trust-requests-them-not-to-attend-11702994834496.html%5C%22%3Emade%20a%20show%20of%20inviting%20the%20two%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20on%20Monday%20was%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-provocateur-in-chief-l-k-advani%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20founded%20in%201980%20and%20Advani%20assumed%20leadership%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20in%201984%20before%20becoming%20party%20president%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20the%20BJP%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpast-continuous-the-birth-of-the-ram-mandir-agitation%5C%22%3E%C2%A0announced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20on%20the%20land%20where%20they%20believed%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20born%20%E2%80%93%20and%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20had%20stood%20for%20over%20400%20years%20%E2%80%93%20was%20its%20key%20political%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20autumn%20of%201990%2C%20Advani%20launched%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Erath%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Somnath%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20which%20was%20to%20stir%20up%20support%20for%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20at%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20mosque%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Shiv%20temple%20had%20stood%20in%20Somnath%20since%20at%20least%20the%206th%C2%A0%C2%A0century%20CE.%20It%20was%20demolished%20and%20reconstructed%20several%20times%20over%20the%20centuries.%20The%20last%20demolition%20came%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20in%201665.%C2%A0It%20lay%20in%20ruins%20until%201950%20when%20its%20reconstruction%20began%20under%20the%20prime%20ministership%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20beginning%20the%20yatra%20at%20Somnath%20and%20ending%20in%20Ayodhya%20thus%20had%20a%20very%20powerful%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0symbolic%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0value%20of%20%E2%80%98reclaiming%E2%80%99%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20was%20done%20in%20Somnath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20in%20his%202008%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcourtneylaportecarm.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fmy-country-my-life-by-lk-advani-foreward-by-atal-bihari-vajpayee.pdf%5C%22%3Ebook%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMy%20Country%20My%20Life%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20choice%20of%20Somnath%20as%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eyatra%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0had%20a%20powerful%20symbolic%20value%2C%20made%20evident%20by%20repeated%20references%20to%20it%20as%20the%20target%20of%20Muslim%20tyranny%20against%20the%20Hindus%E2%80%A6The%20intention%20was%20to%20contextualise%20Ayodhya%20in%20the%20historical%20lineage%20of%20Muslim%20aggression%20and%20then%20to%20seek%20legitimacy%20for%20Mandir%20movement%20by%20drawing%20a%20parallel.%20The%20parallel%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20drew%20was%20with%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20Somnath%20temple.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra%20made%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20not%20carrying%20a%20message%20of%20peace.%20Pictures%20of%20him%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0carrying%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20axe%2C%20a%20sword%20and%20a%20bow%20and%20arrow%20also%20emerged.%20Workers%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20pasted%20posters%20along%20the%20route%20of%20the%20yatra%20of%20the%20proposed%20temple%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3Etreachery%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20course%20of%20the%20yatra%20there%20was%20large%20scale%20violence%2C%20rioting%20and%20killings.%20Advani%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20finally%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flalu-yadav-on-why-and-how-he-arrested-lk-advani-on-october-23-1990-1784734%5C%22%3E%C2%A0stopped%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20arrested%20by%20the%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav-led%20Bihar%20government%20in%20Samastipur%20in%20October%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Advani%2C%20thousands%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0managed%20to%20reach%20Ayodhya%20where%2020%20of%20them%20were%20killed%20after%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20a%20mob%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0led%20by%20a%20coterie%20of%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20were%20led%20by%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705915585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-who-led-ram-janmabhoomi-movement-skips-temple-consecration-citing-extreme-cold%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20had%20reportedly%20told%20him%20and%20his%20colleague%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-who-led-ram-janmabhoomi-movement-skips-temple-consecration-citing-extreme-cold%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Temple%20Construction%20Meant%20Small%20Business%20Owners%20in%20Ayodhya%20Lost%20Money%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Hope%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22132101%2FSG6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyodhya%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%2013-kilometre%20stretch%20of%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20arterial%20road%2C%20newly%20christened%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Path%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20all%20lit%20up%2C%20with%20facades%20of%20each%20building%2C%20home%20and%20shop%20covered%20in%20a%20similar%20set%20of%20symbols%20and%20painted%20a%20uniform%20white%20and%20beige.%20In%20what%20many%20hail%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20development%2C%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20shiny%20new%20roads%20and%20ongoing%20construction%20activities%20have%20all%20focused%20on%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20complex%20%E2%80%93%20built%20after%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20finished%20and%20will%20reportedly%20go%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Fphotos%2Findia-news%2Fram-temple-work-at-ayodhya-in-full-swing-entire-complex-to-be-completed-by-2025%2F%5C%22%3Euntil%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presence%20at%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20has%20been%20advertised%20in%20almost%20every%20corner%2C%20across%20posters%2C%20billboards%20and%20advertisements%20in%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20life%20has%20only%20gone%20from%20%E2%80%9Cbad%20to%20worse%E2%80%9D.%20Sixty-three-year-old%20Gupta%20lives%20in%20the%20locality%20of%20Niyawan%2C%20where%20authorities%20demolished%20dozens%20of%20establishments%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20widening%20the%20stretch%20of%20the%20road%20that%20now%20forms%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Path%E2%80%99.%20A%20former%20grocery%20shop%20owner%2C%20he%20now%20finds%20himself%20struggling%20to%20find%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(the%20SDM%20and%20police)%20came%20at%20night%2C%20we%20were%20not%20even%20given%20a%20prior%20date%2C%20and%20our%20homes%20here%20were%20demolished.%20We%20were%20only%20given%20prior%20information%20about%20them%20looking%20to%20widen%20the%20roads%2C%20but%20we%20had%20no%20idea%20it%20would%20happen%20this%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20beleaguered%20Gupta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20a%20JCB%20bulldozed%20his%20three-storey%20establishment%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20police%20officers%20and%20district%20authorities.%20The%20ground%20floor%20functioned%20as%20a%20grocery%20store%2C%20and%20the%20storeys%20above%20were%20his%20residence%20and%20supplies%20storage%20area.%20More%20than%20a%20year%20since%20the%20demolition%2C%20Gupta%20and%20his%20wife%20now%20live%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20home%20of%20their%20son%2C%20their%20own%20home%20yet%20to%20be%20rebuilt.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20four%20children%20who%20are%20thankfully%20all%20independent.%20If%20they%20were%20still%20in%20school%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20would%20be%20actually%20homeless%20because%20we%E2%80%99d%20have%20nowhere%20to%20live.%20But%20there%20are%20hundreds%20of%20such%20shopkeepers%20in%20this%20area%2C%20in%20Janoura%2C%20Ramnagar%20and%20so%20many%20other%20localities%20who%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20their%20homes%20or%20are%20now%20living%20on%20rent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22122845%2FSG1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22122845%2FSG1.jpg%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22122845%2FSG1-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693961%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22702%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERakesh%20Kumar%20Gupta%20stands%20outside%20the%20remains%20of%20his%20three-storey%20shop%20and%20residence%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20rebuilt%20even%20a%20year%20since%20it%20was%20demolished.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advent%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20has%20given%20the%20entire%20town%20a%20facelift%2C%20with%20the%20building%20and%20widening%20of%20roads%2C%20a%20revamped%20drainage%20system%20and%20railway%20station%2C%20and%20an%20airport.%20These%20changes%20are%20also%20ushering%20in%20a%20boom%20in%20property%20prices%20and%20real%20estate%20deals%2C%20along%20with%20hotel%20owners%20and%20leading%20corporate%20houses%20investing%20in%20this%20new%20temple%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20despite%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fcentralised-monitoring-of-projects-worth-over-rs-30k-crore-in-ayodhya%2Farticleshow%2F97036652.cms%5C%22%3Ewhopping%20Rs%2030%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20spent%20on%20this%20%E2%80%98new%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99%2C%20locals%20like%20Gupta%20are%20now%20paying%20the%20price%20of%20this%20development.%20Gupta%2C%20who%20built%20his%20three-storey%20residence%20in%201998%2C%20estimates%20the%20total%20value%20of%20his%20home%20and%20the%20land%20at%20%E2%80%9CRs%2080%20lakh%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20claims%20that%20authorities%20compensated%20him%20with%20a%20paltry%20Rs%209%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20just%20gave%20us%20compensation%20for%20the%20bricks%2C%20not%20for%20the%20land%20which%20the%20government%20claims%20is%20theirs.%20I%20see%20no%20hope%20of%20getting%20more%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20over%20a%20year%20now.%20They%20also%20said%20they%E2%80%99d%20widen%20the%20road%20by%2010%20metres%2C%20but%20actually%20took%20away%2012%20metres%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20despondently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20shops%20down%20the%20same%20road%20in%20Niyawan%20is%20Satyaprakash%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20small%20storefront.%20The%2045%20year%20old%20also%20owned%20a%20three-storey%20home%2C%20with%20the%20ground%20floor%20serving%20as%20his%20shop%20and%20workplace%2C%20but%20the%20home%20whose%20value%20he%20estimates%20at%20over%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20was%20compensated%20with%20just%20Rs%209%20lakh.%20Even%20as%20he%20used%20the%20compensation%20amount%20to%20rebuild%20his%20shop%2C%20he%20now%20lives%20on%20rent%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20children%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20inability%20to%20rebuild%20the%20upper%20floors%20that%20once%20used%20to%20be%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20only%20earning%20member%20in%20the%20family.%20Ever%20since%20the%20demolition%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20the%20resources%20to%20rebuild%20this%20entirely%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20rent%20a%20place%20for%20us%20to%20live.%20For%2010%20months%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20this%20shop%2C%20I%20drove%20an%20e-rickshaw%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20only%20got%20back%20to%20this%20now%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%20wearily.%20Satprakash%E2%80%99s%20three%20children%20are%20in%20school%20and%20college%2C%20with%20his%20eldest%20son%20having%20to%20stop%20his%20MA%20degree%2C%20because%20he%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20have%20the%20money%20to%20fill%20his%20fees%E2%80%9D.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20364px)%2085vw%2C%20364px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22364%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22485%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESatyaprakash%20Gupta%20sits%20next%20to%20his%20tea%20kiosk%20in%20the%20newly-constructed%20kirana%20shop%20of%20a%20single%20storey%2C%20where%20once%20a%20three-storey%20shop%20as%20well%20as%20his%20family%20home%20existed.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20construction%20and%20painting%20are%20still%20ongoing%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20three%20main%20roads%20now%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Path%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Path%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Bhakti%20Path%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20estimate%20of%20between%204%2C000%20and%204%2C500%20shops%20and%20homes%20have%20been%20broken%20down%20or%20displaced%2C%20according%20to%20Nand%20Kumar%20Gupta%20who%20heads%20the%20Ayodhya%20Udyog%20Vyapar%20Mandal%20traders%E2%80%99%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jalpa%2C%20women%20like%20Sumitra%20Devi%20claimed%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Cprotested%20at%20first%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20have%20now%20been%20silenced%20into%20submission.%20Like%20Rakesh%20and%20Satya%20Prakash%20Gupta%2C%20she%20too%20owned%20a%20home%20and%20shop%20selling%20general%20supplies%2C%20only%20to%20see%20it%20razed.%20When%20contacted%2C%20the%20office%20of%20Ayodhya%20Development%20Authority%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20Vishal%20Singh%20said%20that%20questions%20of%20compensation%20and%20road-building%20were%20under%20the%20district%20magistrate%20and%20PWD%20department%E2%80%99s%20office.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20them%20for%20a%20comment%20and%20this%20story%20shall%20be%20updated%20when%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20Muslim-owned%20businesses%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20economic%20loss%20and%20damages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20lack%20of%20fair%20compensation%20has%20led%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20disillusionment%2C%20many%20shop%20owners%20like%20the%20Guptas%20continued%20to%20echo%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20temple%20would%20bring%20in%20an%20influx%20of%20religious%20tourism%20and%20cash%20flow.%20Despite%20his%20own%20resentment%20at%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20home%20and%20shop%2C%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20Gupta%20expressed%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20Hindus%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20about%20our%20beliefs%20in%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20a%20child%20who%20witnessed%20firsthand%20when%20violence%20broke%20out%20as%20karsevaks%20demolished%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20bound%20to%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20he%20endorsed%20the%20violence%20that%20ensued.%20To%20those%20like%20him%2C%20the%20temple%20itself%20feels%20like%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20faith%20and%20belief%20for%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20separate%20from%20their%20scrambling%20to%20save%20their%20demolished%20homes%20and%20businesses%20destroyed%20under%20the%20proposed%20development%20plan%20for%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20are%20not%20so%20sure%2C%20with%20Muslim-owned%20businesses%20having%20incurred%20losses%20not%20only%20in%20the%20process%20of%20construction%20work%2C%20but%20also%20as%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20temple%20town%20brings%20with%20it%20the%20exclusion%20of%20certain%20professions%20and%20communities.%20Virtually%20every%20shop%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Bakra%20Mandi%20locality%20has%20been%20shut%20for%20the%20past%20week%2C%20with%20butchers%20from%20the%20area%20claiming%20that%20supplies%20that%20came%20from%20Bareilly%20have%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20official%20notice%20or%20orders%2C%20we%20ourselves%20have%20stopped%20work%20for%20this%20week%20because%20devotees%20from%20all%20over%20India%20will%20be%20coming%20here%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20offend%20anyone%20in%20a%20way%20that%E2%80%99ll%20cause%20harm%20to%20our%20shops%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Farid%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20emphasised%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20of%20their%20own%20accord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20meanwhile%20issued%20orders%20for%20the%20closure%20of%20all%20meat%20shops%20in%20the%20state%20on%20January%2022.%20Chief%20secretary%20D.S.%20Mishra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fclosure-of-meat-shops-on-consecration-day-in-uttar-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F106971537.cms%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20directed%20all%20district%20magistrates%20to%20order%20meat%20and%20alcohol%20shops%20to%20remain%20shut%20for%20the%20day.%20While%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Fmeat-liquor-should-not-be-allowed-in-ayodhya-cm-yogi-8663441%2F%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%20emphasised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20that%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20liquor%20will%20be%20banned%20for%20good%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edharamnagri%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20so%20far%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20order%20to%20that%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20a%20prohibition%20on%20selling%20non-veg%20and%20alcohol%20for%20the%204-5%20km%20radius%20around%20the%20temple%2C%20this%20has%20been%20the%20case%20for%20decades%20even%20under%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20butcher%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20start%20of%20notices%20and%20increase%20in%20talks%20with%20district%20administration%20that%20has%20many%20worried%20that%20this%20prohibition%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20expanded%20to%2015%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Irfan%2C%20a%20meat-supplier%20and%20activist%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Tanzimul%20Quraish%20union%20of%20meat-sellers%2C%20said%20that%20as%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Food%20Security%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20department%20had%20sent%20notice%20regarding%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20freshly%20cut%20meat%20in%20the%20open.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20told%20not%20to%20cut%20meat%20in%20the%20open%20on%20the%20roads%20since%20it%20is%20a%20holy%20town%2C%20but%20to%20instead%20sell%20packaged%20frozen%20meat.%20There%20is%20no%20ban%20on%20meat%20as%20such%20yet%2C%20but%20we%20do%20not%20know%20what%E2%80%99ll%20happen%20ultimately.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20going%20to%20become%20clear%20after%20the%2022nd%20of%20January%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20409px)%2085vw%2C%20409px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22409%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3.jpg%20912w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3-228x300.jpg%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3-778x1024.jpg%20778w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693963%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photo%20of%20the%20latest%20notice%20issued%20regarding%20guidelines%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%2C%20even%20as%20no%20official%20ban%20exists.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20no%20official%20ban%2C%20an%20estimated%20150%20to%20175%20butchers%20and%20shops%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20the%20FSDA%20norms.%20Irfan%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20decision%20could%20affect%20the%20livelihood%20of%20more%20than%20500%20families%2C%20especially%20causing%20job%20losses%20to%20those%20establishments%20with%20%E2%80%9C3-4%20extra%20hands%20working%20in%20each%20shop%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Niyawan%2C%20Faizan%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20continues%20to%20operate%20his%20shop%20and%20sell%20freshly%20cut%20meat%20for%20now%2C%20expressed%20concern%20that%20his%20employees%20would%20lose%20out.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20holy%20place%2C%20so%20we%20should%20respect%20sentiments%20by%20not%20cutting%20or%20displaying%20meat%20in%20the%20open.%20I%20understand%20that%20for%20the%20area%20near%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20how%20can%20they%20extend%20this%20for%20up%20to%2015%20km%3F%20Even%20if%20I%20can%20afford%20to%20switch%20to%20prepackaged%20and%20frozen%20meat%2C%20then%20I%20will%20need%20less%20manpower%20and%20will%20have%20to%20fire%20the%20other%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQureshi%20also%20believes%20that%20such%20a%20ban%2C%20if%20implemented%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20in%20correlation%20with%20the%20rise%20in%20hotels%20and%20real%20estate%20ventures.%20With%20hotel%20chains%20like