Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fall-11-convicts-in-bilkis-bano-case-surrender%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twenty-Five%20Years%20Ago%2C%20a%20Murder%20Most%20Foul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22101839%2F22144_w_740_745.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20known%20Gladys%20since%201999%2C%20and%20perhaps%20over%20the%20years%2C%20I%20dare%20call%20myself%20a%20friend%2C%20one%20among%20thousands%20she%20has%20in%20India.%20Some%20call%20her%20the%20most%20well-known%20Christian%20in%20India%2C%20second%20only%20to%20Mother%20Teresa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuppressing%20her%20unfathomable%20pain%20and%20anguish%2C%20she%20told%20television%20reporters%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20forgive%20those%20who%20have%20killed%20my%20husband%20and%20my%20two%20sons.%E2%80%9D%20But%20it%20is%20not%20for%20the%20State%20to%20forgive%2C%20or%20forget%2C%20one%20who%20commits%20a%20murder%20so%20foul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDara%20Singh%2C%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%20from%20the%20Gangetic%20plains%20whose%20usual%20targets%20were%20cow%20traders%20in%20Orissa%2C%20had%20burnt%20alive%20Graham%20Stuart%20Staines%2C%2058%2C%20an%20Australian%20Christian%20missionary%20working%20with%20victims%20of%20leprosy%2C%20and%20his%20two%20sons%2C%20Philip%2C%2010%2C%20and%20Timothy%2C%20aged%206%2C%20as%20they%20slept%20in%20their%20jeep%20in%20a%20forest%20clearing%20in%20Manouharpur-Baripada%20on%20the%20night%20between%20January%2021%20and%2022%2C%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20black%20spot%20on%20the%20nation%2C%20said%20K.R.%20Narayanan%2C%20the%20president%20of%20India%20at%20that%20time%2C%20on%20the%20deed.%20Even%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20expressed%20similar%20feelings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVajpayee%20had%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20earlier%20made%20a%20helicopter%20flight%20to%20Dang%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20where%20members%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20burnt%20about%20three%20dozen%20small%20log%20churches%20in%20the%20bamboo%20and%20sal%20forests%20not%20too%20far%20from%20Surat.%20Back%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20had%20called%20for%20a%20national%20debate%20on%20the%20conversion%20of%20tribals%20to%20Christianity.%20He%20said%20the%20arson%20was%20the%20work%20of%20fringe%20elements%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20more%20than%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVajpayee%20sent%20his%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20George%20Fernandes%2C%20to%20Orissa.%20Fernandes%20went%2C%20returned%20to%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20and%20firmly%20announced%20the%20gruesome%20murders%20were%20by%20a%20foreign%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGladys%20Staines%20is%20still%20involved%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20new%20name%20of%20the%20state.%20Her%20surviving%20child%2C%20a%20daughter%2C%20is%20now%20a%20medical%20doctor%20in%20Australia.%20They%20had%20not%20accompanied%20Graham%20to%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20villages%20that%20fateful%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20when%20the%20murder%20trials%20began%20that%20people%20came%20to%20know%20of%20the%20vicious%20and%20inhumane%20manner%20of%20their%20deaths.%20The%20three%20had%20woken%20up%20when%20the%20flames%20leapt%20from%20their%20vehicles.%20Dara%20Singh%20and%20his%20cohort%20used%20their%20long%2C%20stout%20lathis%20to%20push%20them%20back%20into%20the%20fire%2C%20till%20they%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Staines%E2%80%99%20triple-murders%20was%20when%20the%20western%20world%20came%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20violence%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20India%20by%20religious%20and%20nationalist%20extremists%20groups%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Sangh%20parivar.%20It%20was%20in%202007%20and%202008%20that%20the%20Sangh%20targeted%20Christians%20once%20again%2C%20in%20Kandhamal%20district%20in%20the%20same%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20deaths%2C%20the%20burning%20of%20more%20than%206%2C000%20houses%20and%20300%20churches%20and%20the%20displacement%20of%2060%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Christian%20community%20also%20remembers%20that%20even%20the%20courts%20apparently%20had%20not%20fully%20understood%20the%20murderous%20ideology%20of%20the%20killer.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20which%20finally%20sentenced%20Dara%20Singh%20to%20a%20life%20term%20in%20prison%2C%20said%20the%20murder%20was%20to%20%E2%80%9Cteach%20a%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20missionary.%20It%20was%20the%20strong%20protest%20from%20the%20Christian%20community%20that%20forced%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fdelhi%2Fsc-takes-back-conversion-remark-in-staines-case%2Fstory-WeFdeDep2brkLpgzQ2RGgO.html%5C%22%3Ewithdraw%20those%20deeply%20hurtful%20words%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3EData%3A%20Rise%20in%20Attacks%20on%20Christians%20in%20India%2C%20Up%20Four%20Times%20in%2011%20Years%20(2012-2022)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20upheld%20the%20high%20court%20judgement%20which%20had%20given%20Dara%20Singh%20a%20life%20term%2C%20holding%20that%20the%20crime%20was%20not%20the%20rarest%20of%20the%20rare%2C%20and%20the%20trial%20court%20in%20Khurda%20had%20erred%20in%20giving%20Dara%20Singh%20and%20some%20of%20his%20associates%20the%20death%20penalty%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20undisputed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20interfering%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20belief%20by%20way%20of%20%E2%80%98use%20of%20force%E2%80%99%2C%20provocation%2C%20conversion%2C%20and%20incitement%20or%20upon%20a%20flawed%20premise%20that%20one%20religion%20is%20better%20than%20the%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20civil%20society%20activists%2C%20among%20them%20Navaid%20Hamid%2C%20Shabnam%20Hashmi%2C%20Seema%20Mustafa%2C%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20H.S.%20Hardenia%20and%20former%20MP%20Shahid%20Sidiqi%2C%20and%20Christian%20activists%20including%20this%20writer%2C%20Dominic%20Emmanuel%20and%20Mary%20Scaria%2C%20issued%20an%20angry%20press%20note%2C%20widely%20covered%20in%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Christian%20community%20is%20still%20divided%20on%20its%20support%20or%20opposition%20to%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20but%20most%20in%20the%20Catholic%20and%20Protestant%20churches%20say%20capital%20punishment%20is%20an%20anathema%20in%20this%20age%20and%20time.%20I%20am%20myself%20a%20staunch%20opponent%20of%20the%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20more%20foreigners%20working%20in%20Christian%20relief%20and%20medical%20missions%20in%20the%20country.%20Those%20that%20remain%2C%20old%20men%20and%20women%2C%20have%20become%20citizens.%20But%20%E2%80%9Cpunishing%20conversions%E2%80%9D%20became%20a%20part%20of%20the%20political%20lexicon.%20It%20has%20been%20totally%20weaponised%20now%2C%20used%20not%20just%20against%20Christians%2C%20but%20also%20against%20Muslims.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20main%20instrument%20for%20withdrawing%20the%20FCRA%20licences%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Christian%20NGOs%20which%20were%20working%20on%20donations%20from%20co-religionists%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intimidation%2C%20indeed%20terrorising%2C%20of%20the%20Christian%20community%2C%20continues%20unstopped.%20Its%20victims%20are%20the%20clergy%20and%20mission%20staff%20who%20work%20in%20forest%20and%20tribal%20areas%2C%20among%20Dalits%20and%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20away%20from%20urban%20centres.%20Three%20or%20more%20cases%20of%20anti-Christian%20violence%20took%20place%20every%20day%20in%202023%2C%20the%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20continue%20to%20be%20inactive%20and%20often%20are%20complicit%20in%20the%20state%20of%20lawlessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProbes%20by%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Minorities%2C%20Right%20To%20Information%20(RTI)%20requests%2C%20and%20other%20investigations%20have%20proven%20repeatedly%20there%20have%20been%20no%20fraudulent%20or%20forceful%20conversions%20by%20Christians%20in%20India%20anywhere%2C%20anytime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJohn%20Dayal%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705899620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22101839%2F22144_w_740_745.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgraham-staines-murder-25-years%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20burning%20alive%20of%20Graham%20Stuart%20Staines%20and%20his%20two%20young%20put%20the%20politics%20of%20religious%20hate%2C%20and%20even%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20on%20trial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A178%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgraham-staines-murder-25-years%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20longer%20'Ron%20DeSantimonious'%3A%20Trump%20hails%20'terrific'%20DeSantis%20after%20rival%20ends%20campaign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705895220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-donald-trump-rochester_6429116.jpg%3F20240122072048%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdonald-trump-hails-terrific-ron-desantis-after-rival-ends-campaign-13053766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20described%20one-time%20Republican%20rival%20Ron%20DeSantis%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20terrific%20person%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Florida%20governor%20ended%20his%20presidential%20campaign%20and%20endorsed%20the%20former%20president.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%2