ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20start%20a%20millet-based%20startup%20called%20Health%20Sutra.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20startups%20have%20always%20been%20an%20area%20of%20interest%20for%20Sai.%20%E2%80%9CFood%20tech%20has%20always%20been%20interesting%20to%20me.%20Before%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20I%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Indo-Chinese%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289275%2Fhyderabad-startup-banyan-nation-recycles-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-product-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20my%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20diabetes.%20The%20doctor%20recommended%20various%20alternatives%20such%20as%20wheat%2C%20oats%2C%20or%20quinoa%20for%20his%20diet.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20wonder%20%E2%80%93%20oats%20are%20fine%2C%20but%20quinoa%20is%20imported%20from%20South%20America.%20Why%20opt%20for%20something%20from%20halfway%20across%20the%20world%20when%20we%20have%20equally%20good%20options%20right%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20find%20alternatives%20in%20India%2C%20he%20went%20looking%20for%20options.%20He%20met%20a%20relative%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20food%20science%20department%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20passionately%20discussing%20millets%20and%20how%20they%20are%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20next%20big%20thing.%20Millets%2C%20being%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20our%20land%2C%20boast%20indigenous%20qualities%2C%20robustness%2C%20and%20drought%20resistance%2C%20making%20them%20a%20highly%20beneficial%20c